%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Long%20Queues%2C%20Empty%20Buckets%20In%20%26quot%3BParched%26quot%3B%20Bengaluru%2C%20No%20Water%20Supply%20Tomorrow%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBengaluru%20is%20struggling%20with%20an%20acute%20water%20crisis%20with%20the%20onset%20of%20summer%2C%20prompting%20a%2024-hour%20water%20supply%20cut%20starting%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELow%20water%20levels%20in%20neighbouring%20reservoirs%20and%20receding%20groundwater%20levels%20have%20forced%20the%20city%20water%20board%20to%20prioritize%20other%20water%20sources%2C%20like%20the%20Cauvery%20basin%2C%20to%20meet%20the%20city's%20drinking%20water%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20men%20and%20women%20made%20long%20queues%20with%20empty%20buckets%20to%20collect%20water%20from%20tankers.%20The%20locals%20dependent%20on%20groundwater%20say%20they%20had%20to%20pay%20double%20the%20usual%20cost%20for%20tankers%20to%20meet%20their%20daily%20water%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShimna%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Horamavu%2C%20said%20they%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20use%20the%20groundwater%20for%20a%20month%20and%20are%20now%20dependent%20only%20on%20water%20tankers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20tankers%20charge%20Rs%206%2C000.%20If%20we%20have%20to%20pay%20this%20price%20every%20day%2C%20it%20will%20become%20very%20difficult%20for%20us.%20Our%20savings%20are%20affected%20as%20we%20are%20paying%20both%20for%20drinking%20water%20and%20for%20water%20for%20other%20daily%20needs.%20We%20will%20be%20happy%20if%20the%20authorities%20help%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Chief%20Minister%20DK%20Shivakumar%20said%20the%20government%20is%20exploring%20the%20possibility%20of%20digging%20more%20borewells%20to%20solve%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20allotted%20Rs%208%20crore%20to%20solve%20the%20water%20issue.%20Some%20MLAs%20said%20borewells%20have%20been%20dug%20up%20to%201%2C500%20feet.%20We%20are%20exploring%20the%20possibility%20of%20digging%20500%20meters%20deeper%20besides%20installing%20more%20borewells%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Shivakumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20MLA%20Byrathi%20Basavaraj%2C%20who%20represents%20the%20KR%20Puram%20constituency%2C%20slammed%20the%20government%20for%20solving%20the%20water%20crisis%20despite%20multiple%20representations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20water%20scarcity%20everywhere.%20What%20is%20the%20government%20doing%3F%20I%20have%20written%20so%20many%20letters.%20All%20guarantees%20are%20being%20given%20but%20there%20is%20no%20money%20for%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708934820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fa6lfjos_bengaluru-water-shortage_625x300_26_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2F24-hour-water-supply-cut-tomorrow-as-bengaluru-runs-dry-ahead-of-summer-5129388%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bengaluru%20is%20struggling%20with%20an%20acute%20water%20crisis%20with%20the%20onset%20of%20summer%2C%20prompting%20a%2024-hour%20water%20supply%20cut%20starting%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2F24-hour-water-supply-cut-tomorrow-as-bengaluru-runs-dry-ahead-of-summer-5129388%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2F24-hour-water-supply-cut-tomorrow-as-bengaluru-runs-dry-ahead-of-summer-5129388%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2F24-hour-water-supply-cut-tomorrow-as-bengaluru-runs-dry-ahead-of-summer-5129388%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arrest%20Trinamool%20Strongman%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%2C%20Says%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20order%20stopping%20Bengal%20Police%20from%20arresting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsheikh-shahjahan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESheikh%20Shahjahan%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20the%20main%20accused%20in%20sexual%20assault%20and%20land%20grab%20allegations%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsandeshkhali%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESandeshkhali%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20clarify%20there%20is%20no%20stay%20on%20arrest%20in%20any%20proceeding.%20There%20is%20only%20a%20first%20information%20report%20and%20he%20(Shahjahan)%20has%20been%20named%20as%20an%20accused.%20Obviously%20he%20needs%20to%20be%20arrested%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court's%20clarification%20comes%20after%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fabhishek-banerjee%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAbhishek%20Banerjee%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20an%20astonishing%20claim%20Sunday%20night%20-%20that%20the%20Bengal%20government%20is%20unable%20to%20arrest%20Shahjahan%20because%20the%20court%20had%20%26quot%3Btied%20the%20hands%20the%20police%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20comments%20slammed%20by%20the%20opposition%20BJP%20as%20%26quot%3Bcontempt%20of%20court%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Banerjee%20seemed%20to%20blame%20the%20High%20Court%20for%20delaying%20the%20Sandeshkhali%20inquiries%20-%20by%20staying%20its%20order%20to%20form%20a%20SIT%20to%20probe%20the%20January%205%20attack%20on%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20told%20today%2043%20FIRs%20were%20registered%20till%20December%20last%20year%2C%20of%20which%2042%20had%20resulted%20in%20charge-sheets.%20%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20grabbing%20land%20of%20tribal%20community%20members%2C%20seven%20cases%20were%20started%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20was%20told%2C%20%26quot%3BSince%20February%208%2C%2024%20cases%20of%20land%20grabbing%20and%20various%20sections%20were%20filed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%20the%20court%20observed%20drily%2C%20%26quot%3BSurprising%20no%20arrests%20were%20made%20in%20four%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%20Mr%20Banerjee%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B...those%20calling%20for%20Shahjahan's%20arrest%20should%20make%20an%20appointment%20and%20ask%20the%20court%20why%20this%20stay%20was%20granted.%20Was%20it%20to%20ensure%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20could%20secure%20mileage%20from%20this%20incident%3F%26quot%3B%20and%20insisted%20the%20Trinamool%20is%20not%20shielding%20its%20on-the-run%20strongman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20High%20Court%20ties%20hands%20of%20state%20administration%20(then)%20what%20can%20be%20done%3F%20After%20the%20January%205%20incident%20-%20when%20it%20was%20claimed%20ED%20officers%20were%20attacked%20-%20the%20central%20agency%20filed%20a%20complaint%20and%20the%20High%20Court%20ordered%20the%20constitution%20of%20a%20SIT%20with%20state%20police%20and%20central%20agencies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAround%2010-12%20days%20later%20ED%20appealed%20for%20stay%20in%20the%20High%20Court.%20The%20plea%20was%20accepted.%20This%20means%20they%20did%20not%20want%20any%20investigation%2C%20arrest%2C%20summons%2C%20or%20interrogation%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Banerjee%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20High%20Court%20ties%20hands%20of%20state%20police%2C%20how%20can%20they%20arrest%20anyone%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked%20again%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20arrests%20of%20Trinamool%20leaders%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F17-people-arrested-so-far-in-sandeshkhali-incident-mamata-banerjee-5065395%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUttam%20Sardar%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftrinamool-leader-shibu-hazra-arrested-after-complaints-of-sexual-harassment-by-women-in-bengals-sandeshkhali-5076506%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShibu%20Hazra%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20put%20this%20on%20record...%20Trinamool%20is%20not%20guarding%20Shahjahan.%20Judiciary%20is.%20Lift%20the%20stay%20and%20see%20what%20police%20does%20next...%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Banerjee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court's%20next%20hearing%20in%20this%20case%20had%20been%20set%20for%20March%206%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Banerjee%20also%20said%20the%20authorities%20had%20to%20be%20given%20%26quot%3Bat%20least%20a%20month%26quot%3B%20to%20make%20arrests%2C%20and%20referred%20to%20the%20alleged%20Saradha%20chit%20fund%20scam%2C%20into%20which%20the%20ED's%20inquiries%20began%20in%202013.%20He%20claimed%20a%20%26quot%3Bdual%20policy%26quot%3B%20and%20claimed%20the%20state%20police%20force%20never%20not%20get%20similar%20leeway%20in%20its%20investigations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%20of%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20have%20rebutted%20Mr%20Banerjee's%20arguments%2C%20pointing%20out%20the%20court%20had%20not%20issued%20a%20stay%20on%20investigative%20process%2C%20or%20the%20arrest%20of%20any%20individual%2C%20including%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Banerjee's%20comments%20-%20which%20came%20after%20Bengal%20Police%20arrested%20party%20leader%20Ajit%20Maity%20on%20charges%20of%20grabbing%20land%20from%20villagers%20-%20were%20labelled%20by%20opposition%20leaders%20as%20contempt%20of%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshahjahan-sheikh-trinamool-leader-ajit-maity-arrested-in-sandeshkhali-over-land-grab-charges-5128337%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrinamool%20Leader%20Ajit%20Maity%20Arrested%20In%20Sandeshkhali%20Land%20Grab%20Case%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20not%20from%20the%20Government.%20He%20is%20speaking%20on%20behalf%20of%20his%20party.%20He%20is%20the%20shining%20jewel%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress.%20The%20Trinamool%20cannot%20remove%20Shahjahan%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP's%20Samik%20Bhattacharya%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Mr%20Banerjee's%20attacks%20did%20not%20stop%20wi