ighlighting%20the%20'gross%20injustice'%20done%20to%20the%20country's%20youth%20seeking%20regular%20employment%20in%20the%20armed%20forces%2C%20Kharge%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20future%20of%20nearly%202%20lakh%20young%20men%20and%20women%20has%20become%20uncertain%20due%20to%20the%20ending%20of%20the%20regular%20recruitment%20process%20in%20the%20armed%20forces%26quot%3B.%20He%20claimed%20that%20these%20youths%20spent%20years%20in%20pursuit%20of%20their%20dream%20and%20%26quot%3Bthe%20resulting%20frustration%20and%20hopelessness%20has%20even%20led%20to%20several%20reported%20deaths%20by%20suicide%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20High%20Court%20Rejected%20Challenge%20To%20Hindu%20Prayers%20In%20Gyanvapi%20Cellar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mulayam%20Singh%20government's%201993%20move%20to%20stop%20Hindu%20prayers%20in%20one%20of%20the%20cellars%20of%20Varanasi's%20Gyanvapi%20Mosque%20was%20%26quot%3Billegal%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20said%20today%2C%20rejecting%20a%20petition%20challenging%20a%20district%20court%20order%20that%20allowed%20the%20prayers%20to%20resume%20after%2030%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cellar%2C%20known%20as%20Vyas%20Ji%20Ka%20Tehkhana%2C%20was%20sealed%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20Demolition%20in%201992.%20Soon%20after%20the%20demolition%2C%20then%20chief%20minister%20Kalyan%20Singh%20had%20resigned%20and%20his%20government%20was%20subsequently%20dismissed%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20President's%20Rule.%20In%20the%20Assembly%20polls%20next%20year%2C%20a%20government%20headed%20by%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20took%20over.%20The%20state%20government%20then%20cited%20law%20and%20order%20concerns%20and%20the%20cellar%20temple%20was%20sealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20district%20court's%20order%20last%20month%2C%20allowing%20resumption%20of%20Hindu%20prayers%20in%20the%20cellar%2C%20came%20on%20a%20petition%20by%20Shailendra%20Pathak%20Vyas.%20Mr%20Vyas%20had%20then%20submitted%20that%20his%20family%20held%20prayers%20in%20the%20cellar%20since%20the%20British%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20worship%20and%20rituals%20which%20continued%20to%20be%20performed%20in%20the%20cellar%20by%20Vyas%20family%20till%201993%20was%20stopped%20by%20illegal%20action%20of%20State%20without%20there%20being%20any%20order%20in%20writing%2C%26quot%3B%20today's%20high%20court%20judgment%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArticle%2025%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20grants%20freedom%20of%20religion.%20The%20Vyas%20family%20who%20continued%20performance%20of%20religious%20worship%20and%20rituals%20in%20the%20cellar%20could%20not%20be%20denied%20access%20by%20oral%20order.%20A%20citizen%20right%20guaranteed%20under%20Article%2025%20cannot%20be%20taken%20away%20by%20arbitrary%20action%20of%20State%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20said%20Shailendra%20Pathak%20Vyas%20has%20said%20the%20cellar%20has%20been%20in%20his%20family's%20possession%20since%201551%20and%20had%20submitted%20documents%20to%20show%20how%20it%20was%20willed%20down%20the%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20a%201936%20map%20filed%20by%20the%20then%20state%20government%20showed%20the%20Vyas%20ji%20ka%20tehkana.%20The%20court%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20Committee%20Of%20Management%20Anjuman%20Intezamia%20Masjid%2C%20which%20challenged%20the%20district%20court%20order%2C%20had%20failed%20to%20establish%20prima%20facie%20possession%20over%20the%20cellar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFailure%20of%20appellant%20to%20establish%20prima%20facie%20possession%20over%20the%20disputed%20property%2C%20and%20plaintiff%20succeeding%20in%20building%20up%20a%20strong%20prima%20facie%20case%20negating%20the%20stand%20of%20appellant%2C%20leads%20to%20undeniable%20situation%20that%20stopping%20worship%20and%20performance%20of%20rituals%20by%20the%20devotees%20in%20the%20cellar%20would%20be%20against%20their%20interest%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrima%20facie%20I%20find%20that%20act%20of%20the%20State%20Government%20since%20year%201993%20restraining%20Vyas%20family%20from%20performing%20religious%20worship%20and%20rituals%20and%20also%20by%20the%20devotees%20was%20a%20continues%20wrong%20being%20perpetuated%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Rohit%20Ranjan%20Agarwal%20said%20in%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20noted%20that%20an%20attempt%20was%20made%20to%20malign%20the%20image%20of%20the%20lower%20court%20%26quot%3Bon%20the%20ground%20that%20the%20officer%20concerned%20had%20passed%20the%20order%20on%20last%20day%20of%20working%26quot%3B.%20It%20noted%20that%20the%20district%20court%20had%20already%20asked%20the%20administration%20to%20take%20control%20in%20an%20order%20dated%20January%2017%2C%202024%20and%20the%20January%2031%20order%20was%20only%20to%20correct%20an%20accidental%20slip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsidering%20the%20overall%20submissions%20advanced%20by%20the%20respective%20counsel%20of%20the%20parties%20and%20after%20analysing%20the%20material%20on%20record%2C%20I%20find%20that%20the%20appellant%20has%20not%20made%20out%20any%20case%20for%20interfering%20in%20the%20order%20dated%2017.01.2024%20and%2031.01.2024%20appointing%20the%20District%20Magistrate%2C%20Varanasi%20as%20Receiver%20and%20arranging%20to%20carry%20out%20worship%20and%20rituals%20in%20Vyas%20tehkhana%20(cellar)%20under%20his%20supervision%20by%20the%20priest%2C%20so%20appointed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20prayers%20in%20the%20cellar%20started%20on%20February%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708934460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fflvhvic_gyanvapi-cellar_625x300_01_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.n