0reasons%20behind%20the%20extension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20a%20FasTag%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFasTag%20is%20an%20electronic%20toll%20collection%20system%20introduced%20in%20India%20to%20streamline%20and%20automate%20the%20toll%20payment%20process%20on%20highways.%20It%20utilises%20Radio-Frequency%20Identification%20(RFID)%20technology%20through%20a%20sticker%20or%20tag%20affixed%20to%20a%20vehicle's%20windshield.%20This%20tag%20is%20linked%20to%20the%20user's%20prepaid%20or%20savings%20account%2C%20allowing%20for%20automatic%20deduction%20of%20toll%20charges%20as%20the%20vehicle%20passes%20through%20equipped%20toll%20plazas.%20FasTag%20enhances%20the%20efficiency%20of%20toll%20collection%20by%20eliminating%20the%20need%20for%20manual%20payments%2C%20reducing%20travel%20time%2C%20and%20contributing%20to%20fuel%20savings.%20Its%20interoperable%20nature%20ensures%20a%20seamless%20experience%20across%20various%20toll%20plazas%20in%20the%20country.%20Users%20can%20conveniently%20recharge%20their%20FasTag%20accounts%20online%2C%20and%20its%20implementation%20aims%20to%20promote%20digital%20payments%20and%20alleviate%20congestion%20at%20toll%20booths%2C%20ultimately%20improving%20the%20overall%20travel%20experience%20on%20Indian%20highways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFive%20Paytm%20FASTag%20alternatives%20you%20can%20consider%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.NHAI%20FASTag%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ENHAI%20FasTag%20is%20a%20bank-neutral%20version%2C%20meaning%20it%20isn't%20linked%20to%20a%20specific%20bank%20when%20purchased%20and%20can%20be%20obtained%20from%20designated%20points%20like%20toll%20plazas%2C%20petrol%20pumps%2C%20online%20platforms%2C%20or%20through%20the%20My%20FasTag%20app%20and%20popular%20e-commerce%20sites%20like%20Amazon%20or%20Flipkart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%