n%20against%20the%20policemen%20who%20are%20guilty%20of%20badly%20beating%20up%20an%20unarmed%20youngster%20who%20was%20just%20serving%20langar%20to%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Punjab%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20remark%20by%20a%20BJP%20leader%20criticising%20the%20Haryana%20police's%20actions%20to%20stop%20the%20farmers%20marching%20towards%20Delhi.%20The%20farmers%20have%20been%20protesting%20over%20several%20demands%2C%20including%20a%20law%20to%20guarantee%20a%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20(MSP)%20for%20their%20crops.%20MSP%20is%20the%20minimum%20price%20at%20which%20a%20crop%20can%20be%20bought%20and%20acts%20as%20a%20price%20guarantee%20for%20farmers%2C%20protecting%20them%20from%20distress%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMultiple%20rounds%20of%20talks%20between%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20farmers%20have%20failed%20to%20find%20a%20breakthrough.%20While%20the%20Centre%20has%20agreed%20to%20provide%20an%20MSP%20guarantee%2C%20there%20is%20disagreement%20over%20the%20formula%20according%20to%20which%20it%20would%20be%20provided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana%20police%20have%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20fortified%20the%20state'%20borders%20with%20Punjab%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20farmers%20cannot%20proceed%20towards%20Delhi.%20They%20have%20used%20teargas%20shells%20every%20time%20the%20farmers%20have%20approached%20the%20barricades%20blocking%20the%20way.%20A%2021-year-old%20farmer%2C%20Shubhkaran%20Singh%2C%20died%20during%20a%20clash%20between%20the%20cops%20and%20the%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20farmer%20leader%20Sarwan%20Singh%20Pandher%20slammed%20Haryana%20police%20over%20the%20injuries%20to%20Pritpal%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmer%20leader%20Baldev%20Singh%20Sirsa%20said%20Pritpal%20Singh%20were%20doing%20%26quot%3Blangar%20seva%26quot%3B%20at%20Khanauri%20when%20he%20was%20allegedly%20dragged%20by%20the%20policemen.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20dragged%20from%20his%20tractor