%20World%20Again%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20decade%20after%20a%2019.88-carat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhunt-for-stolen-kashmir-sapphire-takes-mysterious-turn-1267415%5C%22%3EKashmir%20sapphire%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frare-kashmir-sapphire-fetches-rs-2-8-crore-at-us-auction-483035%5C%22%3Eshattered%20auction%20records%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Geneva%2C%20the%20potential%20return%20of%20the%20priceless%20gems%20from%20the%20strife-torn%20region%20to%20global%20markets%20is%20on%20the%20horizon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cushion-shaped%20sapphire%2C%20known%20as%20the%20Star%20of%20Kashmir%2C%20surprised%20buyers%20in%202013%20with%20a%20sale%20price%20of%20nearly%20%243%2C483%2C017%20(approximately%20Rs%2020%20crore).%20Now%2C%20officials%20claim%20that%20more%20peacock%20blue-coloured%20sapphires%20will%20be%20mined%20in%20the%20Paddar%20region%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20inhospitable%20terrains%20in%20the%20bordering%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2Febl152bo_sapphire-gemstone-is-the-best-for-these-zodiac-signs-know-about-them_625x300_02_March_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cstrong%3E(Photo%20for%20representation)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcolonial-era-file-sheds-light-on-indian-gems-and-jewels-in-uks-royal-treasury-3928509%5C%22%3EKashmir%20sapphires%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20revered%20as%20among%20the%20finest%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20resurgence%20in%20the%20Kashmiri%20economy%20marks%20a%20significant%20shift%2C%20seemingly%20overcoming%20longstanding%20hurdles%20related%20to%20mining%20and%20marketing%20rights.%20It's%20reliably%20learned%20that%20local%20traders%2C%20previously%20resistant%20to%20outsider%20involvement%20in%20mining%20and%20marketing%20the%20gems%2C%20had%20persistently%20demanded%20exorbitant%20prices%2C%20hindering%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20landscape%20is%20evolving.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20pivotal%20moment%20for%20these%20sapphires%20came%20after%20traders%20from%20Kashmir%20were%20advised%20by%20the%20state-owned%20Gems%20and%20Jewellery%20Export%20Promotion%20Council%20(GJEPC)%20to%20adhere%20to%20global%20trade%20norms.%20In%20essence%2C%20they%20were%20advised%20to%20auction%20the%20gems%2C%20mirroring%20the%20international%20diamond%20trade%2C%20and%20evaluate%20offers%20from%20buyers.%20The%20traders%20have%20since%20embraced%20this%20guidance%2C%20which%20emanated%20from%20the%20Commerce%20Ministry%20through%20the%20GJEPC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKashmir%20sapphires%20are%20very%20unique.%20Mining%20and%20trading%20of%20these%20gems%20need%20to%20be%20streamlined%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sabyasachi%20Ray%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20GJEPC.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20explained%20to%20those%20involved%20with%20the%20trading%20of%20sapphires%20the%20importance%20of%20doing%20the%20business%20methodically%20and%20as%20per%20international%20norms.%20The%20traders%20should%20not%20be%20raising%20unrealistic%20demands%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EKashmir's%20Tryst%20With%20Gems%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20implementing%20such%20measures%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20India's%20most%20troubled%20state%20bordering%20Pakistan%2C%20poses%20considerable%20challenges.%20The%20allure%20of%20gems%20has%20historically%20captivated%20tribes%20spanning%20the%20vast%20stretch%20between%20Afghanistan%20and%20Kashmir.%20Gemstones%20have%20long%20been%20understood%20as%20transformative%20assets%20by%20tribal%20communities%20in%20Afghanistan%20and%20Pakistan.%20GJEPC%20officials%20caution%20that%20Kashmiri%20traders%20could%20still%20resist%20conforming%20to%20international%20guidelines%2C%20potentially%20reverting%20to%20old%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecognising%20the%20sensitivity%20surrounding%20gem%20trade%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20GJEPC%20is%20diligently%20navigating%20these%20complexities%2C%20cognisant%20of%20the%20pivotal%20role%20local%20traders%20play.%20The%20Himalayan%20region's%20gems%20boast%20a%20rich%20historical%20lineage%2C%20extending%20from%20India%20to%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsider%20Afghanistan's%20gem%20mining%20heritage%2C%20which%20dates%20back%20approximately%202%2C300%20years%20to%20the%20era%20of%20Alexander%20the%20Great.%20By%20the%2010th%20century%2C%20the%20gem%20mines%20of%20northern%20and%20eastern%20Afghanistan%2C%20bordering%20Tajikistan%20and%20Pakistan%2C%20were%20famed%20for%20their%20rubies%2C%20sapphires%2C%20tourmaline%2C%20lapis%20lazuli%2C%20and%20topaz.%20Today%2C%20gem%20mines%20in%20northeastern%20Afghan%20provinces%20serve%20as%20revenue%20sources%20for%20the%20Taliban%20regime.%20Similarly%2C%20in%20neighbouring%20Pakistan%2C%20gem%20mining%20and%20trade%20remain%20contentious%2C%20often%20sparking%20tensions%20over%20the%20extraction%20of%20high-value%20gemstones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EA%20Determined%20Government%20To%20Go%20Ahead%20With%20Mining%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20is%20determined%20to%20avoid%20such%20controversies%20in%20Kashmir.%20The%20government%2C%20specifically%20the%20Commerce%20Ministry%2C%20has%20set%20up%20a%20detailed%20roadmap%20for%20mining%20sapphires%20from%20Kashmir.%20A%20preliminary%20survey%20for%20the%20sapphire%20mines%20in%20the%20Paddar%20region%20has%20been%20completed%20by%20the%20Geological%20Survey%20of%20India%20(GSI).%20Now%2C%20there%20will%20be%20scientific%20exploration%20of%20the%20area.%20Extreme%20geographical%20conditions%20and%20lack%20of%20resources%20have%20hampered%20the%20commercial%20exploitation%20of%20this%20valuable%20stone.%20The%20status%20of%20the%20preliminary%20survey%20was%20discussed%20by%20top%20officials%20at%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20board%20of%20directors%20of%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Minerals%20Limited%20here%2C%20chaired%20by%20the%20state's%20chief%20secretary%20Arun%20Mehta.%20A%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20some%20of%20the%20sapphires%20were%20taken%20to%20Jaipur%20for%20display%20at%20an%20exhibition%20where%20the%20Kashmir%20sapphires%20generated%20tremendous%20interest%20among%20the%20traders%20of%20the%20desert%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20top%20official%20of%20the%20state%20told%20this%20reporter%20the%20Kashmir%20stones%20are%20considered%20unique%20across%20the%20world%2C%20even%20better%20than%20the%20ones%20found%20in%20Mogok%2C%20Myanmar.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Kashmir%20sapphires%20are%20the%20best%20in%20the%20world%20and%20we%20will%20be%20seeking%20the%20best%20price%20for%20them.%20Plans%20for%20mining%20are%20firmly%20in%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20Arun%20Kishore%20Kotwal%2C%20a%20top%20official%20of%20the%20mining%20department%20in%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%2C%20said%20in%20a%20telephonic%20interview.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKotwal%20said%20the%20Kashmir%20blue%20peacock-coloured%20sapphires%20are%20in%20limited%20quantities%20and%20will%20be%20produced%20in%20phases.%20The%20total%20amount%20of%20sapphires%20to%20be%20mined%20would%20be%20in%20the%20region%20of%20Rs%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A3000-4000%5C%22%20data-linkindex%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20data-auth%3D%5C%22NotApplicable%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E3%2C000-4%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0crore.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20then%20we%20will%20work%20on%20the%20next%20phase%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Kotwal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJKML%2C%20it%20has%20been%20reliably%20learnt%2C%20has%20awarded%20the%20exploration%20of%20sapphire%20mines%20to%20Mineworks%2C%20a%20Delhi-based%20company.%20Mineworks%20will%20jointly%20execute%20the%20project%20with%20JKML.%20The%20move%2C%20however%2C%20has%20triggered%20some%20anger%20among%20the%20business%20community%20in%20Kishtwar%2C%20which%20did%20not%20like%20an%20%E2%80%9Coutsider%E2%80%9D%20being%20granted%20the%20contract.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Mineworks%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20affected.%20Managed%20by%20the%20Tongya%20family%2C%20the%20company%20is%20among%20the%20top%20Indian%20gems%20companies%20with%20footprints%20across%20the%20world.%20Recently%2C%20one%20of%20its%20subsidiaries%20acquired%20an%20extremely%20rare%2C%20high-quality%20Zambian%20emerald%20that%20was%20sold%20at%20an%20auction%20in%20Lusaka%20for%20an%20undisclosed%20amount.%20The%20gemstone%2C%20gorgeously%20green%20and%20wonderfully%20translucent%2C%20was%20christened%20Insofu%2C%20which%20means%20'baby%20elephant'%20in%20the%20local%20Bemba%20language%20of%20Zambia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%206%2C100%20carats%20and%201%2C220%20gm%2C%20the%20gem%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20emeralds%20to%20be%20mined%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20specialises%20in%20blue%20sapphires%2C%20boasting%20fascinating%20collections%20of%20blue-coloured%20stones%2C%20among%20them%20two%20rare%2C%20flawless%20oval-shaped%20sapphires%20%E2%80%94%20called%20the%20Sunburst%20Sapphires%20%E2%80%94%20weighing%20151.15%20carat%20and%20127.68%20carat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20All%20Are%20Satisfied%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20not%20everyone%20in%20the%20state%20is%20happy%20with%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20state%20government%20to%20collaborate%20with%20a%20Delhi-based%20company.%20The%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Industries%20and%20Commerce%20Department%20feels%20that%20JKML%20could%20have%20avoided%20the%20joint%20venture%20and%20done%20the%20mining%20on%20its%20own.%20Other%20business%20associations%20in%20the%20state%20have%20also%20expressed%20dissatisfaction%20with%20the%20agreement.%20Commerce%20Ministry%20officials%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20such%20fears%20from%20the%20state%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20acknowledges%20the%20importance%20and%20class%20of%20these%20gems.%20Market%20experts%20say%20Asia%20has%20some%20of%20the%20best%20gems%20across%20the%20world%2C%20with%20Kashmir%20leading%20in%20peacock%20blue%20sapphires%2C%20followed%20by%20Myanmar%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Thailand%2C%20Vietnam%2C%20Cambodia%2C%20Madagascar%2C%20and%20Australia.%20The%20Kashmir%20sapphire%2C%20claim%20experts%2C%20displays%20a%20unique%20character%20that%20signifies%20the%20most%20desirable%20and%20expensive%20of%20gems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Landslide%20And%20A%20Treasure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20wanted%20to%20take%20charge%20of%20the%20princely%20state%20of%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%2C%20but%20their%20attempts%20were%20thwarted%20by%20the%20then%20Maharaja%20Ranbir%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20loyal%20to%20the%20empire%20but%20denied%20them%20authoritative%20privileges%20over%20his%20land%20and%20people.%20Interestingly%2C%20four%20years%20before%20the%20Maharaja's%20death%20in%201881%2C%20a%20landslide%20occurred%20in%20a%20harsh%20and%20remote%20cirque%20valley%20of%20the%20Zanskar%20range.%20At%2013%2C000%20feet%20above%20sea%20level%2C%20the%20landslip%20exposed%20a%20100-feet%20wide%20area%20of%20pegmatitic%20rock%20with%20blue%20crystals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sapphires%20were%20first%20traced%20in%201881%20by%20some%20local%20traders%20who%20lived%20in%20the%20valleys%20of%20Zanskar%20and%20Lahul.%20They%20traded%20the%20gems%20for%20salt.%20By%201882%2C%20parcels%20of%20blue%20gemstones%20began%20to%20reach%20Delhi%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20across%20India.%20The%20Maharaja%20became%20extremely%20concerned%20about%20the%20lost%20fortune%20and%20immediately%20ordered%20his%20army%20of%20soldiers%20to%20guard%20the%20mines.%20Eventually%2C%20the%20British%20government%20took%20charge%20of%20the%20mines.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20original%20old%20mine%2C%20which%20produced%20a%20limited%20assortment%20of%20high-quality%20and%20large-size%20Kashmir%20sapphires%2C%20was%20entirely%20depleted%20in%201888.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThereafter%2C%20some%20of%20the%20gems%20were%20traded%20at%20the%20marketing%20centres%20of%20Kullu%20and%20Shimla%20by%20a%20syndicate%20of%20jewellers.%20Eventually%2C%20the%20Geological%20Survey%20of%20India%20concurred%20with%20the%20discovery%20of%20sapphires%20in%20a%20glacial%20cirque%20above%20the%20village%20of%20Sumjam%2C%20on%20the%20southwest%20slopes%20of%20the%20rugged%20Zanskar%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Commerce%20Ministry's%20Intervention%20Is%20Timely%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20work%20of%20exploration%20and%20security%20of%20mineral%20wealth%20and%20assets%20is%20looked%20after%20by%20the%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20Mineral%20Limited.%20There%20have%20been%20occasions%20when%20the%20operations%20of%20JKML%20have%20drawn%20flak%20from%20local%20traders%2C%20many%20even%20alleging%20that%20it%20undertook%20mining%20operations%20but%20there%20was%20no%20clarity%20about%20the%20collection%20of%20the%20gems.%20As%20per%20rules%2C%20the%20mining%20operation%20needs%20to%20be%20completed%20between%20July%201%20and%20September%2018%2C%202024.%20Thereafter%2C%20the%20gems%20will%20be%20sent%20for%20processing%20into%20finished%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Commerce%20Ministry's%20intervention%20is%20both%20crucial%20and%20timely%20because%20there%20have%20been%20occasions%20when%20the%20exposed%20mineral%20wealth%20was%20stolen%20by%20smugglers.%20Now%2C%20the%20ministry%20hopes%20its%20intervention%20and%20that%20of%20the%20state%20government%20will%20stop%20such%20smuggling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%C2%A0Kumar%2C%20SP%20Kishtwar%2C%20has%20clarified%20recently%20to%20mediapersons%20that%20there%20were%20a%20few%20reports%20of%20smuggling%2C%20but%20it%20has%20stopped.%20A%20few%20smugglers%20have%20been%20booked%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20mines%20are%20buried%20under%20ten%20feet%20of%20snow.%20And%20there%20is%20high%20security.%20Once%20the%20area%20opens%20up%20by%20the%20end%20of%20May%2C%20mining%20will%20start.%20And%20then%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20top-class%20sapphires%20will%20make%20its%20way%20to%20the%20Indian%20and%20global%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shantanu%20Guha%20Ray%20is%20the%20Asia%20Editor%20of%20Central%20News%20Agency.%20His%20book%20'The%20Diamond%20Trial'%20came%20out%20in%202019).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708926900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2Febl152bo_sapphire-gemstone-is-the-best-for-these-zodiac-signs-know-about-them_625x300_02_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fkashmiri-sapphires-set-to-dazzle-the-world-yet-again-5128759%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20decade%20after%20a%2019.88-carat%20Kashmir%20sapphire%20shattered%20auction%20records%20in%20Geneva%2C%20the%20potential%20return%20of%20the%20priceless%20gems%20from%20the%20strife-torn%20region%20to%20global%20markets%20is%20on%20the%20horizon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fkashmiri-sapphires-set-to-dazzle-the-world-yet-again-5128759%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fkashmiri-sapphires-set-to-dazzle-the-world-yet-again-5128759%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fkashmiri-sapphires-set-to-dazzle-the-world-yet-again-5128759%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hindu%20'puja'%20to%20continue%20in%20Gyanvapi%20cellar%3A%20Allahabad%20HC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708926887000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108001091%2Cimgsize-1709450.cms%22%2C%22originI