akistan-sindh-punjab-to-decide-their-chief-ministers-today%2Famp_articleshow%2F108001207.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-sindh-punjab-to-decide-their-chief-ministers-today%2Famp_articleshow%2F108001207.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Curfew%20Imposed%20In%20Maharashtra's%20Ambad%20Amid%20Maratha%20Quota%20Agitation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20curfew%20has%20been%20imposed%20in%20Ambad%20taluka%20of%20Maharashtra's%20Jalna%20district%20to%20prevent%20any%20law%20and%20order%20issue%20in%20view%20of%20the%20ongoing%20agitation%20for%20Maratha%20reservation%20by%20activist%20Manoj%20Jarange%2C%20as%20per%20an%20order%20issued%20by%20the%20district%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJalna%20collector%20Srikrushna%20Panchal%20in%20the%20order%20said%20Jarange%20announced%20on%20Sunday%20that%20he%20will%20go%20to%20Mumbai%20and%20agitate%20over%20his%20demand%20of%20reservation%20for%20the%20Maratha%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20possibility%20that%20quota%20supporters%20may%20arrive%20at%20Antarwali%20Sarati%20village%20in%20Ambad%20taluka%20of%20Jalna%2C%20where%20the%20activist%20has%20been%20staging%20a%20hunger%20strike%2C%20to%20stop%20him%20(from%20going%20to%20Mumbai).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20huge%20crowd%2C%20there%20is%20a%20possibility%20that%20traffic%20on%20Dhule-Mumbai%20highway%20and%20tehsils%20near%20Ambad%20may%20be%20affected%2C%20the%20order%20mentioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20may%20impact%20peace%20and%20create%20law%20and%20order%20issues.%20Hence%2C%20curfew%20has%20been%20imposed%20under%20CrPC%20section%20144%20(2)%20by%20the%20district%20collector%20in%20Ambad%20taluka%20from%20Monday%20midnight%20till%20further%20orders%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernment%20offices%2C%20schools%2C%20movement%20on%20national%20highways%2C%20milk%20distribution%2C%20media%20and%20hospitals%20are%20exempted%20from%20this%20order%2C%20the%20collector%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJarange%20on%20Sunday%20night%20left%20from%20Antarwali%20Sarati%20and%20reached%20nearby%20Bhamberi%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20on%20Monday%20morning%2C%20the%20protesting%20activist%20returned%20to%20Antarwali%20Sarati%20and%20started%20taking%20medical%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20speaking%20in%20Antarwali%20Sarati%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Jarange%20alleged%20that%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20was%20trying%20to%20kill%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJarange%20also%20announced%20that%20he%20would%20march%20to%20Mumbai%20and%20protest%20outside%20the%20residence%20of%20the%20deputy%20CM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20also%20said%20a%20poisoning%20attempt%20was%20made%20against%20him%20through%20saline%2C%20though%20he%20did%20not%20elaborate%20on%20the%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20on%20Sunday%20said%20Jarange%20must%20not%20test%20the%20patience%20of%20his%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShinde%20also%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party-Sharadchandra%20Pawar%20chief%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20while%20responding%20to%20Jarange.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wonder%20why%20Jarange's%20speech%20looks%20like%20the%20script%20generally%20used%20by%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%26quot%3B%20Shinde%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20legislature%20during%20a%20one-day%20special%20session%20last%20Tuesday%20unanimously%20passed%20a%20bill%20providing%2010%20per%20cent%20reservation%20for%20the%20Marathas%20in%20education%20and%20government%20jobs%20under%20a%20separate%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Jarange%20has%20been%20firm%20on%20his%20demand%20for%20quota%20for%20the%20community%20under%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Class%20(OBC)%20category%20and%20converting%20the%20notification%20on%20'blood%20relatives'%20of%20Kunbi%20Marathas%20into%20a%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20budget%20session%20of%20the%20state%20legislature%20will%20be%20held%20from%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708926780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fe86d8nko_maharashtra-ambad-_625x300_26_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaratha-quota-agitation-manoj-jarange-curfew-imposed-in-maharashtras-ambad-amid-maratha-quota-agitation-5128662%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20curfew%20has%20been%20imposed%20in%20Ambad%20taluka%20of%20Maharashtra's%20Jalna%20district%20to%20prevent%20any%20law%20and%20order%20issue%20in%20view%20of%20the%20ongoing%20agitation%20for%20Maratha%20reservation%20by%20activist%20Manoj%20Jarange%2C%20as%20per%20an%20order%20issued%20by%20the%20district%20administration.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaratha-quota-agitation-manoj-jarange-curfew-imposed-in-maharashtras-ambad-amid-maratha-quota-agitation-5128662%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaratha-quota-agitation-manoj-jarange-curfew-imposed-in-maharashtras-ambad-amid-maratha-quota-agitation-5128662%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaratha-quota-agitation-manoj-jarange-curfew-imposed-in-maharashtras-ambad-amid-maratha-quota-agitation-5128662%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%20woman%20in%20Arabic%20print%20dress%20saved%20from%20mob%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708926724000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F7455%2Fproduction%2F_132718792_4ee607ae-3557-421c-b72d-0b6274802c26.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%