ng%20in%20Haryana's%20Jhajjar%20district.%20Rajesh%20has%20told%20police%20in%20his%20complaint%20that%20Mr%20Rathi%2C%20his%20maternal%20uncle%2C%20was%20sitting%20on%20the%20front%20left%20seat%2C%20right%20next%20to%20him%2C%20in%20the%20Toyota%20Fortuner%20SUV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rear%20seat%20was%20occupied%20by%20a%20gunner%20posted%20in%20the%2066-year-old%20INLD%20leader's%20security%20and%20a%20party%20colleague%2C%20Jaikishan%20Dalal.%20The%20SUV%20was%20waiting%20at%20the%20Barahi%20railway%20crossing%20on%20the%20way%20to%20Bahadurgarh%20when%20a%20car%20stopped%20behind%20it.%20Five%20men%20approached%20the%20SUV%20and%20fired%20at%20least%2020%20rounds%2C%20Rajesh%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20complaint%2C%20one%20of%20the%20shooters%20told%20Rajesh%20after%20the%20firing%20stopped%2C%20%26quot%3BTujhe%20zinda%20chor%20rahe%20hain%2C%20jake%20inke%20ghar%20bata%20diyo%20(we%20are%20sparing%20you%2C%20go%20and%20tell%20his%20family.)%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20basis%20of%20Rajesh's%20complaint%2C%20police%20have%20registered%20a%20case%20of%20murder%20against%20seven%20people%2C%20including%20BJP%20leader%20Naresh%20Kaushik%2C%20and%20several%20relatives%20of%20Bahadurgarh%20municipal%20corporation%20chaiperson%20Saroj%20Rathi.%20Charges%20of%20criminal%20conspiracy%20and%20Arms%20Act%20have%20also%20been%20slapped%20against%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECCTV%20footage%20from%20the%20vicinity%20has%20shown%20an%20i20%20car%20tailing%20the%20SUV%20Mr%20Rathi%20was%20travelling%20in.%20The%20same%20camera%20has%20captured%20the%20car%20returning%20about%2020%20minutes%20later.%20Police%20suspect%20the%20killers%20came%20in%20this%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20broad%20daylight%20shooting%20has%20sent%20shockwaves%20through%20Haryana%20and%20sparked%20criticism%20for%20the%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20government%20months%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20and%20state%20elections.%20INLD%20leader%20Abhay%20Chautala%20has%20alleged%20that%20Mr%20Rathi%2C%20the%20party's%20Haryana%20chief%2C%20had%20asked%20for%20more%20security%20months%20back%2C%20but%20it%20was%20not%20provided.%20The%20Congress%20and%20AAP%2C%20too%2C%20have%20slammed%20the%20state%20government%20over%20the%20shocking%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20a%20single%20culprit%20involved%20in%20this%20case%20will%20be%20spared.%20Police%20have%20been%20instructed%20to%20arrest%20the%20accused%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%20and%20take%20the%20strictest%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Minister%20Khattar%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708924800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F89pipllo_nafe-singh-rathi_625x300_26_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnafe-singh-rathi-nafe-singh-rathee-haryana-shooting-sparing-your-life-go-tell-his-family-killers-told-inld-leaders-nephew-5128700%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20nephew%20of%20Nafe%20Singh%20Rathi%20was%20at%20the%20wheel%20when%20the%20Indian%20National%20Lok%20Dal%20(INLD)%20leader%20was%20riddled%20with%20bullets%20last%20afternoon%20near%20a%20Railway%20crossing%20in%20Haryana's%20Jhajjar%20district%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnafe-singh-rathi-nafe-singh-rathee-haryana-shooting-sparing-your-life-go-tell-his-family-killers-told-inld-leaders-nephew-5128700%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnafe-singh-rathi-nafe-singh-rathee-haryana-shooting-sparing-your-life-go-tell-his-family-killers-told-inld-leaders-nephew-5128700%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnafe-singh-rathi-nafe-singh-rathee-haryana-shooting-sparing-your-life-go-tell-his-family-killers-told-inld-leaders-nephew-5128700%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kenneth%20Mitchell%20dies%20after%205-y