an%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETill%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fshows%2Fndtv-special-ndtv-24x7%2Fwatch-ndtv-s-1999-kargil-war-coverage-aired-july-2006-713848%5C%22%3EKargil%20War%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20was%20a%20long-accepted%20practice%20that%20the%20bodies%20of%20Indian%20soldiers%20who%20were%20slain%20in%20action%20would%20not%20be%20sent%20home%20but%20cremated%20near%20the%20battlefield.%20However%2C%20there%20was%20one%20instance%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fshows%2Fgreat-battles%2Fthe-battle-of-1962-aired-august-2005-297517%5C%22%3E1963%20when%20a%20soldier's%20remains%20were%20sent%20to%20his%20home%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20February%2018%2C%201963%20thousands%20of%20people%20gathered%20in%20Jodhpur%20to%20celebrate%20the%20final%20journey%20of%20a%20national%20hero%2C%20the%20hero%20of%20Chushul%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajnath-singh-to-inaugurate-revamped-rezang-la-war-memorial-in-ladakh-official-2607439%5C%22%3EMajor%20Shaitan%20Singh%2C%20PVC.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2018%2C%201962%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frichly-decorated-border-security-force-camels-add-dazzle-to-republic-day-parade-4935378%5C%22%3ECharlie%20Company%20of%2013%3C%2Fa%3E%20Kumaon%20fought%20one%20of%20the%20fiercest%20battles%20the%20Indian%20Army%20had%20ever%20been%20engaged%20in%2C%20at%20Rezang%20La.%20The%20company%20was%20commanded%20by%20Major%20Shaitan%20Singh%2C%20who%20went%20missing%20in%20action%20along%20with%20113%20of%20his%20fellow%20soldiers.%20The%2013%20Kumaon%20would%20still%20be%20based%20in%20Durbuk%20till%20February.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThree%20Months%20Later...%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20week%20of%20February%2C%20a%20local%20Ladakhi%20shepherd%20and%20his%20herd%20of%20cattle%20were%20passing%20across%20the%20Rezang%20La%20region%20when%20he%20was%20stunned%20by%20the%20sight%20of%20what%20he%20saw%3A%20combatants%20frozen%20to%20death%2C%20still%20holding%20their%20damaged%20weapons.%20Their%20guns%20bulged%20from%20constant%20fire%20and%20were%20mostly%20empty.%20He%20rushed%20to%20notify%20the%20closest%20Army%20unit%2C%20a%20few%20kilometres%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%20and%20the%20government%20focused%20mostly%20on%20the%20news.%20A%20week%20later%2C%20on%20February%2012%2C%201963%2C%20the%20first%20Indian%20party%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%20and%20the%20International%20Red%20Cross%2C%20armed%20with%20motion%20and%20still%20cameras%20from%20the%20Press%20Information%20Bureau%2C%20ascended%20Rezang%20La.%20Brig.%20T.N.%20Raina%20was%20in%20command%20of%20the%20search%20team%2C%20which%20also%20included%20Lieutenant%20Colonel%20H.S.%20Dhingra%2C%20AVSM%2C%20Subedar%20Major%20Changdi%20Ram%2C%20Major%20Girish%20Narayan%20Sinha%2C%20the%20Battalion%202-IC%2C%20and%20a%20number%20of%20other%20officials%2C%20along%20with%20soldiers%20from%2013%20Kumaon.%20The%20adjutant%20of%201%20Jat%20(LI)%20Captain%20K.S.%20Kang%20had%20specifically%20requested%20his%20CO%20to%20allow%20him%20to%20join%20the%20search%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Major%20Shaitan%20Singh%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Major%20Shaitan%20Singh%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Ffgep7nao_shaitan-singh_625x300_26_February_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajor%20Shaitan%20Singh%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20Courtesy%3A%20Jai%20Samota%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20team%20arrived%20at%20the%20summit%2C%20what%20they%20saw%20was%20beyond%20belief.%20One%20could%20actually%20see%20the%20bunkers%20and%20fortifications%20that%20had%20been%20demolished%20by%20Chinese%20artillery.%20Sandbags%20had%20been%20torn%20apart%20by%20bullets%20and%20splinters%2C%20and%20fragments%20of%20these%20bullets%20and%20artillery%20ammunition%20were%20scattered%20around%20the%20scene.%20The%20team%20also%20saw%20the%20martyred%20soldiers'%20bullet-%20and%20splinter-riddled%20bodies%2C%20still%20holding%20firearms%20firmly%20in%20their%20hands.%20Dharampal%20Dhaiya%2C%20the%20nursing%20assistant%2C%20still%20had%20a%20bandage%20and%20a%20morphine%20syringe%20in%20his%20hands.%20He%20lost%20his%20life%20aiding%20a%20fellow%20soldier.%20The%20company's%20headquarters%20had%20sustained%20heavy%20shelling%20during%20the%20last%20strike.%20Major%20Shaitan%20Singh's%20body%20had%20not%20been%20found%20up%20to%20this%20time.%20All%20the%20victims%20had%20been%20shot%20in%20the%20front%2C%20no%20one%20had%20been%20shot%20in%20the%20back%20while%20trying%20to%20flee.%20They%20perished%20as%20heroes%20in%20battle.%20When%20Brig%20T.N.%20Raina%20realised%20this%2C%20he%20was%20in%20tears.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajor%20Shaitan%20Singh's%20radio%20operator%2C%20Sep.%20Ram%20Chander%2C%20helped%20locate%20his%20body.%20It%20was%20near%20the%20area%20where%20Ram%20Chander%20and%20the%20two%20Havildars%20last%20saw%20him.%20His%20body%20was%20still%20resting%20on%20a%20boulder%2C%20and%20his%20hands%20held%20an%20LMG%20with%20the%20trigger%20depressed.%20Wild%20birds%20had%20feasted%20on%20his%20nose%20and%20eyes%20already%2C%20and%20the%20terrible%20cold%20turned%20his%20entire%20face%20black.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Bodies%20of%20soldiers%20being%20carried%20back%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Bodies%20of%20soldiers%20being%20carried%20back%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fbd7sb1i8_shaitan-singh_625x300_26_February_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBodies%20of%20soldiers%20being%20carried%20back%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20Courtesy%3A%20Jai%20Samota%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20body%20was%20found%20to%20have%20eight%20bullet%20holes%2C%20mostly%20in%20and%20around%20his%20left%20arm%20and%20the%20abdomen.%20Bodies%20of%20as%20many%20as%2097%20soldiers%2C%20including%20Major%20Shaitan%20Singh%2C%20were%20found%20till%20February%2013.%20Removing%20the%20weapons%20from%20their%20hands%20required%20cutting%20off%20the%20fingers%2C%20so%20tightly%20were%20they%20gripped.%20The%20bodies%20were%20carried%20down%20with%20the%20assistance%20of%20borrowed%20yaks%20and%20ponies.%20Major%20Shaitan%20Singh's%20family%20was%20informed%20that%20his%20remains%20were%20expected%20to%20arrive%20in%20Palam%20on%20February%2015%20and%20that%20they%20might%20be%20able%20to%20attend%20his%20funeral%20at%20Delhi%20Cantonment%20the%20same%20day.%20On%20February%2015%2C%20Major%20Shaitan%20Singh's%20remains%20were%20taken%20to%20Fukche%20Airfield%20after%20being%20accorded%20a%20guard%20of%20honour%20in%20Chushul.%20Major%20Rewat%20Singh%2C%20a%20friend%20from%20school%2C%20who%20was%20in%20command%20of%20a%20company%20of%209%20Dogra%2C%20was%20present%20at%20the%20airstrip.%20He%20received%20his%20friend's%20mortals%2C%20with%20whom%20he%20had%20grown%20up%2C%20with%20a%20heavy%20heart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajor%20Shaitan%20Singh's%20body%20was%20to%20be%20flown%20from%20Fukche%20to%20Delhi%20-%20where%20the%20cremation%20was%20scheduled%20-%20in%20a%20special%20ice-packed%20casket%20inside%20a%20transport%20aircraft%20operated%20by%20No.%2019%20TPT%20Squadron.%20The%20Major's%20family%20travelled%20to%20Jodhpur%20from%20their%20village.%20Eventually%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Col%20Mohan%20Singh%20and%20Lieutenant-General%20Bikram%20Singh%2C%20who%20issued%20the%20directive%20to%20bring%20the%20Major's%20remains%20to%20Jodhpur%2C%20the%20same%20aircraft%20that%20was%20scheduled%20to%20travel%20to%20Delhi%20took%20off%20for%20Jodhpur.%20And%20that%20was%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%20that%20the%20remains%20of%20a%20soldier%20were%20sent%20to%20his%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Major%20Shaitan%20Singhs%20funeral%20procession%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Major%20Shaitan%20Singhs%20funeral%20procession%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fcpbtkeio_shaitan-singh_625x300_26_February_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20gather%20for%20Major%20Shaitan%20Singh's%20funeral%20procession%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20Courtesy%3A%20Jai%20Samota%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20aircraft%20landed%20at%20the%20Jodhpur%20Airfield%20at%2015%3A42.%20A%20large%20crowd%20had%20gathered.%20The%20General%20Officer%20Commanding%20(GOC)%20of%20Delhi%20and%20Rajasthan%20area%20received%20the%20body%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20then%20Rajasthan%20Chief%20Minister%20Mohanlal%20Sukhadia.%20The%20coffin%20was%20carried%20by%20the%20Army%20and%20Air%20Force%20officers%20on%20their%20shoulders.%20As%20many%20as%20175%20soldiers%20paid%20their%20respects%20to%20the%20Paramvir%20at%20the%20airstrip%20with%20a%20guard%20of%20honour.%20The%20coffin%20was%20delivered%20to%20Colonel%20Mohan%20Singh's%20residence.%20As%20he%20had%20requested%2C%20the%20Major's%20body%20was%20to%20be%20sent%20to%20his%20home%2C%20not%20the%20village.%20His%20eyes%20welling%20with%20grief%2C%20he%20spoke%20as%20he%20received%20the%20body%2C%20%26quot%3BShaitan%20Singh%20is%20my%20commanding%20officer%20as%20of%20right%20now%3B%20I%20was%20his%20until%20this%20moment.%26quot%3B%20Narpat%2C%20who%20had%20been%20called%20from%20Ajmer%2C%20came%20to%20Jodhpur%20upon%20learning%20of%20his%20father's%20demise.%20He%20hugged%20him%20and%20cried%20when%20he%20saw%20the%20body%2C%20wrapped%20in%20white%20cloth.%20The%20body%20was%20then%20taken%20outside%2C%20where%20thousands%20of%20people%20gathered%20as%20the%20last%20rites%20began%20later.%20The%20route%20taken%20by%20the%20procession%20was%20five%20miles%20long.%20On%20either%20side%20of%20the%20street%2C%20thousands%20of%20people%20gathered.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20gather%20to%20pay%20their%20respects%20to%20Shaitan%20Singh%5C%2