20says%20he's%20turned%20his%20lifestyle%20into%20a%20business%20that%20covers%20his%20costs%20%E2%80%94%26nbsp%3Bhere's%20how.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225472%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20on%20bicycle%20with%20Gran%20Canaria%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d624f2a610a9069d5ae47c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETristan%20Ridley%20has%20been%20cycling%20around%20the%20world%20full%20time%20for%208%20years.%3Cp%3ETristan%20Ridley%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETristan%20Ridley%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bbikepacker%26quot%3B%20who%20has%20been%20traveling%20the%20world%20for%20eight%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20his%20first%20year%20on%20the%20road%2C%20he%20was%20living%20off%20less%20than%20%2410%20a%20day.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERidley%20turned%20his%20passion%20into%20a%20business%2C%20offering%20coaching%20services%20to%20aspiring%20bikepackers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETristan%20Ridley%20was%20days%20into%20his%20first%20long-distance%20trip%20when%20he%20met%20with%20a%20life-threatening%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20just%20crossed%20a%20river%20by%20foot%2C%20and%20was%20pulling%20up%20his%20bicycle%20to%20the%20shore%2C%20when%20a%20group%20of%20men%20drinking%20asked%20him%20to%20stop.%20People%20he%20had%20talked%20to%20about%20Papua%20New%20Guinea%20had%20warned%20him%20not%20to%20stop%20in%20a%20situation%20like%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20got%20straight%20back%20on%20my%20bike%20and%20I%20cycled%20past%20them.%20I%20just%20kind%20of%20gave%20them%20a%20wave%2C%20and%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20saw%20me%2C%20they%20immediately%20got%20to%20their%20feet.%20They%20started%20running%20at%20me%20shouting%20%E2%80%94%20most%20of%20them%20had%20machetes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ridley%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20video%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20managed%20to%20get%20away%20and%20carried%20on%20with%20his%20trip%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20cycling%20from%20Papua%20New%20Guinea%20all%20the%20way%20back%20home%20to%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELiving%20on%20%246%20a%20day%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERidley%2C%20now%2033%2C%20is%20a%20full-time%20%E2%80%9Cbikepacker%E2%80%9D%20who%20has%20been%20traveling%20the%20world%20for%20eight%20years.%20He%20started%20using%20bikes%20to%20travel%20in%202015%20and%20has%20since%20ridden%20the%20lengths%20of%20Africa%2C%20Asia%2C%20Europe%2C%20and%20nearly%20all%20of%20Oceania.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20solo%20travels%20started%20with%20nights%20in%20hostels%20and%20traveling%20by%20buses%20and%20trains.%20From%20there%2C%20he%20moved%20into%20hitchhiking%20and%20camping.%20Wanting%20even%20more%20flexibility%2C%20he%20began%20considering%20cycling.%20After%20a%20few%20painful%20trips%2C%20it%20became%20his%20vehicle%20of%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20do%20this%20big%20trip%2C%20which%20I%20figured%20would%20take%20about%20a%20year.%20I%20had%20saved%20just%20enough%20from%20part%20time%20work%20in%20Australia%20that%20I%20could%20manage%20it%20on%20a%20very%20tight%20budget%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20his%20first%20long-distance%20trip%20which%20covered%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20China%2C%20Central%20Asia%2C%20and%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221075%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tristan%20Ridley%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d62a75a3bd891424f8ea0b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22972%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERidley%20enjoys%20his%20first%20beer%20after%20crossing%20China%2C%20after%20three%20weeks%20of%20no%20breaks%20and%20no%20showers.%3Cp%3ETristan%20Ridley%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20really%20don't%20need%20much%20money%20to%20travel%20very%20long%20distances%20on%20a%20bicycle.%20In%20my%20first%20year%20I%20was%20living%20on%20about%20five%20pounds%2C%20or%20%246.30%2C%20a%20day%2C%20slightly%20less%20even%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ridley%20said.%20He%20budgeted%204%2C000%20pounds%2C%20or%20%245%2C048%2C%20for%20the%20year-long%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERidley%20has%20done%20most%20of%20his%20traveling%20solo.%20He%20said%20that%20depending%20on%20himself%20through%20road%20accidents%20and%20visa%20troubles%20has%20made%20him%20mentally%20tough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere's%20times%20when%20I'm%20very%20grateful%20to%20be%20alone%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ridley%20said.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20personal%20growth%2C%20I%20think%20traveling%20solo%20has%20enormous%20value.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20traveling%20alone%20taught%20him%20how%20to%20improvise%2C%20be%20comfortable%20under%20pressure%2C%20and%20how%20to%20deal%20with%20people.%20In%20terms%20of%20security%2C%20he%20finds%20that%20personal%20skills%20and%20forming%20accurate%20judgments%20are%20his%20%E2%80%9Cfirst%20line%20of%20defense%E2%80%9D%20and%20more%20useful%20than%20knives%20or%20pepper%20spray.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaking%20a%20business%20out%20of%20his%20passion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224003%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20pyramid%20in%20Egypt.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d627daf533b039a885a437%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222459%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERidley%20has%20cycled%20the%20lengths%20of%20four%20continents%20since%20he%20began%20in%20end-2015.%3Cp%3ETristan%20Ridley%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Ridley%20spent%20more%20time%20on%20the%20road%2C%20more%20people%20started%20reaching%20out%20to%20him%20looking%20for%20advice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20getting%20to%20the%20point%20where%20I%20just%20felt%20like%20I%20didn't%20really%20have%20the%20time%20anymore%20to%20reply%20to%20all%20of%20these%20messages%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20decided%20to%20start%20a%20coaching%20service%20and%20