%20They're%20about%20two%20hours%20away%20from%20the%20nearest%20airport%2C%20mall%2C%20and%20movie%20theater%2C%20Fraser%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20foreigners%20can't%20own%20land%20in%20the%20Philippines%2C%20Fraser%20signed%20a%2025-year%20leasehold%20contract%20on%20the%20land%20instead%2C%20with%20the%20right%20to%20extend%20his%20lease%20for%20an%20additional%2025%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inside%20the%20house%20during%20construction.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cb05c06fcb546d2d4eeade%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20interiors%20of%20the%20house%20during%20construction.%3Cp%3ECorey%20Fraser%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20people%20always%20say%20that%20I%20could%20get%20in%20trouble.%20And%20I'm%20like%2C%20'Well%2C%2050%20years%20after%20I'm%2040%2C%20sure.'%20But%20if%20I'm%20around%20at%2090%2C%20I'll%20probably%20be%20in%20the%20city%20near%20a%20hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20Fraser%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDesigning%20the%20home%20on%20his%20own%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20land%20is%20850%20square%20meters%2C%20or%20about%209%2C100%20square%20feet%2C%20while%20the%20couple's%20loft-style%20house%20measures%20a%20little%20over%202%2C100%20square%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFraser%20spent%20about%20%24110%2C000%20building%20the%20entire%20home.%20He%20designed%20the%20place%20on%20his%20own%20before%20enlisting%20an%20architect%20to%20create%20the%20blueprints%20for%20the%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20actually%20drew%20it%20on%20my%20computer.%20I%20was%20doing%20this%20for%20different%20types%20of%20automotive%20facilities%20in%20the%20past%2C%20so%20while%20I%20had%20never%20designed%20a%20house%2C%20I%20was%20pretty%20good%20with%20the%20software%20and%20setting%20everything%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Fraser%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223023%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20exterior%20of%20the%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cb03e96fcb546d2d4eeac5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222267%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20exterior%20of%20the%20house.%3Cp%3ECorey%20Fraser%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20floor%20of%20the%20house%20is%20where%20the%20living%20room%2C%20the%20kitchen%2C%20the%20dining%20area%2C%20an%20office%2C%20a%20bathroom%2C%20and%20a%20spare%20bedroom%20are.%20The%20second%20floor%20is%20where%20the%20master%20bedroom%20and%20bathroom%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20started%20building%20the%20home%20in%202017%2C%20even%20before%20they%20moved%20to%20the%20Philippines%20because%20they%20wanted%20it%20to%20be%20mostly%20ready%20by%20the%20time%20they%20arrived.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20got%20all%20of%20that%20done%2C%20including%20the%20pool%20and%20the%20tile%20work%20before%20I%20moved%20here%2C%20and%20then%20we%20finalized%20plumbing%20and%20electrical%20when%20I%20got%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Fraser%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EChallenges%20building%20the%20house%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20bigger%20challenges%20he%20faced%20during%20the%20construction%20process%20involved%20finding%20the%20right%20crew.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAround%20here%2C%20they%20would%20generally%20build%20houses%20very%20cheaply%20and%20they%20would%20try%20to%20do%20it%20quickly%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20want%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Fraser%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20living%20area.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cafbe194aa8ee8e84a803b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20living%20area.%3Cp%3ECorey%20Fraser%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20local%20contractors%20had%20a%20different%20practice%20when%20it%20came%20to%20fixing%20mistakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20West%2C%20if%20the%20contractor%20doesn't%20do%20a%20good%20job%2C%20he's%20starting%20it%20over%20for%20free.%20He's%20fixing%20it%20to%20do%20it%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhereas%20now%20if%20I%20didn't%20like%20something%2C%20he%20goes%2C%20'Well%20you%20can%20pay%20me%20again%20to%20do%20it%20next%20month.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDebt-free%20living%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20house%20is%20hooked%20up%20to%20the%20power%20grid%2C%20but%20the%20couple%20installed%20solar%20panels%20for%20electricity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20although%20they're%20connected%20to%20the%20mains%20water%20supply%2C%20they%20also%20put%20in%20a%20well%20on%20their%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20plan%20for%20moving%20over%20here%20was%20not%20to%20have%20a%20mortgage%2C%20nor%20an%20electric%20bill%2C%20nor%20a%20car%20payment.%20Lastly%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20also%20grow%20at%20least%20part%20of%20my%20own%20food%20because%20those%20are%20your%20highest%20expenses%20over%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Fraser%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20vegetables%20they%20eat%20are%20grown%20in%20their%20own%20garden%2C%20he%20said.%20They%20also%20have%20over%2040%20chickens%2C%20which%20they're%20rearing%20for%20eggs%20and%20meat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20healthier%20and%20happier%20life%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kitchen%20and%20dining%20area.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cb058294aa8ee8e84a8096%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20kitchen%20and%20dining%20area.%3Cp%3ECorey%20Fraser%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20over%20two%20years%20since%20Fraser%20moved%20to%20the%20Philippines%2C%20and%20he%20says%20he's%20much%20happier%20and%20healthier%20than%20he%20used%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLiving%20in%20Chicago%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20not%20blaming%20Chicago%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20was%20on%20blood%20pressure%20medication%20in%20my%2030s%20and%20now%20my%20blood%20pressure%20is%20lower%20than%20it's%20ever%20been%2C%20and%20I'm%20not%20even%20on%20any%20medication%2C%26quot%3B%20Fraser%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20pace%20of%20life%20has%20slowed%20down%20dramatically%2C%20and%20since%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-moved-to-philippines-debt-free-slow-life-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecost%20of%20living%20in%20the%20Philippines%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20much%20more%20affordable%20than%20in%20the%20US%2C%20he%20doesn't%20feel%20as%20stressed%20as%20he%20used%20to%20be%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222056%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20pool.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d55b97a610a9069d5ac62f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221542%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20pool.%3Cp%3ECorey%20Fraser%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20running%20in%20the%20rat%20race%20back%20in%20the%20States%20just%20working%20nonstop%20to%20pay%20bills%20and%20then%20start%20it%20all%20over%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20wasn't%20going%20to%20be%20rich%2C%20but%20I%20was%20comfortable%20every%20month%20having%20more%20than%20I%20would%20need%20in%20the%20Philippines.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Fraser%20has%20a%20new%20hobby%3A%20He's%20been%20documenting%20his%20journey%20moving%20to%20and%20living%20in%20the%20Philippines%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40ItsMe_Philippines%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20what%20motivates%20him%20to%20share%20about%20his%20own%20experiences%20is%20to%20inspire%20others%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20goal%20the%20whole%20time%20was%20to%20create%20a%20life%20that%20I%20don't%20need%20to%2