t-124022500415_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20Has%20Allowed%20its%20Authority%20to%20Be%20Diluted%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25222448%2FSupreme-Court-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFormer%20Delhi%20high%20court%20judge%20Justice%20Rekha%20Sharma%20delivered%20the%20following%20remarks%20at%20a%20seminar%20organised%20by%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3Ethe%20Campaign%20for%20Judicial%20Accountability%20and%20Reforms%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3Cem%3Eand%20%3C%2Fem%3ELiveLaw%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20thankful%20to%20the%20organisers%20for%20having%20provided%20me%20with%20this%20opportunity%20to%20be%20with%20you%20all%20today.%20Though%20I%20am%20almost%20a%20stranger%20to%20the%20actual%20working%20of%20the%20Roster%20system%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20let%20me%20share%20my%20own%20little%20experience%20of%20what%20I%20have%20heard%20and%20observed.%20The%20subject%20has%20taken%20me%20back%20to%20the%20year%20I%20enrolled%20myself%20as%20an%20Advocate.%20That%20was%20the%20day%20my%20family%20looked%20at%20me%20with%20awe%20and%20amazement.%20It%20was%20because%20none%20of%20them%20except%20my%20father%20had%20ever%20seen%20a%20court%20room.%20My%20resolve%20to%20practice%20law%20was%20difficult%20for%20them%20to%20digest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnowing%20none%2C%20and%20with%20no%20brief%2C%20I%20would%20sit%20in%20some%20court%20room%20or%20the%20other%2C%20listen%20to%20the%20arguing%20counsel%20and%20comeback%20home%20briefless%20and%20with%20empty%20pocket.%20But%2C%20then%2C%20miracles%20do%20happen.%20It%20was%20a%20Friday.%20I%20saw%20an%20elderly%20lady%20lawyer%20getting%20up%2C%20bowing%20her%20head%2C%20and%20saying%20something.%20Two%20serious%20looking%20judges%20raised%20their%20heads%2C%20looked%20at%20her%2C%20%E2%80%9CDismissed%E2%80%9D%2C%20said%20their%20Lordships.%20The%20lady%20lawyer%20passed%20by%20my%20seat%2C%20red%20faced%2C%20head%20jerking%2C%20murmuring%20something%20inaudible.%20While%20she%20lost%20her%20brief%2C%20it%20made%20my%20day.%20It%20carved%20my%20future.%20I%20followed%20her%20to%20her%20chamber%2C%20introduced%20myself%2C%20told%20her%20I%20was%20watching%20her%20great%20performance%2C%20and%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20her%20junior.%20She%20looked%20at%20me%2C%20asked%20me%20to%20have%20a%20seat%2C%20and%20agreed%20to%20take%20me%20as%20her%20junior.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20long%20time%2C%20I%20would%20carry%20her%20bulky%20files%2C%20follow%20her%20from%20one%20court%20room%20to%20another%2C%20and%20became%20immune%20to%20the%20epithets%2C%20good%20or%20bad%20for%20the%20different%20Benches.%20However%2C%20one%20thing%20is%20clear%20to%20me.What%20was%20earlier%20being%20said%20in%20whispering%20tones%2C%20in%20present%20times%20is%20being%20talked%20openly.%20And%2C%20it%20is%20something%20called%20%E2%80%9CBench%20fixing%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20with%20the%20passage%20of%20time%20I%20became%20a%20busy%20lawyer%2C%20the%20Bench%20and%20its%20allure%20became%20overwhelming.%20I%20was%20selected%20for%20the%20Higher%20Judicial%20Service%2C%20and%20a%20few%20years%20later%20elevated%20to%20the%20Bench.%20However%2C%20somewhere%20in%20the%20back%20of%20my%20mind%2C%20the%20epithet%20%E2%80%9CBench%20fixing%E2%80%9D%20kept%20haunting.%20And%2C%20to%20my%20surprise%20and%20dismay%2C%20I%20realized%20that%20though%20in%20the%20High%20Court%2C%20the%20Registry%E2%80%99s%20hands%20were%20clipped%20by%20the%20Roster%20System%2C%20that%20system%20too%20was%20not%20free%20from%20rat%E2%80%99s%20smell.%20And%20that%20smell%20emanated%20principally%20from%20the%20pen%20of%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20who%20was%20incharge%20of%20the%20Roster.%20None%20of%20the%20so-called%20Service%20Judges%20was%20ever%20assigned%20important%20constitutional%20matters%2C%20habeas%20corpus%20or%20other%20writ%20petitions%20involving%20important%20questions%20of%20law.%20All%20such%20cases%20went%20to%20judges%20directly%20elevated%20from%20the%20Bar.%20As%20if%2C%20the%20judges%20from%20the%20Bar%20were%20paragon%20of%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Narasimha%20Rao%E2%80%99s%20bribery%20case%20which%20revolved%20around%20the%20interpretation%20of%20Article%20105%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20and%20involving%20not%20only%20the%20person%20who%20held%20the%20position%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20but%20other%20equally%20important%20persons%2C%20showed%20not%20only%20the%20judge%E2%80%99s%20indefatigable%20courage%2C%20but%20also%20his%20complete%20grasp%20over%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%20and%20its%20interpretation.%20But%2C%20what%20is%20important%20in%20the%20present%20context%20is%20that%20the%20author%20of%20the%20judgement%20was%20a%20service%20judge.%20Make%20no%20mistake%2C%20the%20case%20was%20not%20assigned%20to%20him.%20It%20landed%20before%20him%20because%20he%20happened%20to%20be%20sitting%20in%20a%20criminal%20roster%2C%20and%20the%20question%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20interpretation%20of%20Article%20105%20of%20the%20Constitution%20arose%20out%20of%20that%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20what%20is%20the%20present%20state%20of%20affairs%2C%20particularly%20in%20Supreme%20Court.%20It%20has%20taken%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20more%20than%20five%20years%20to%20decide%20Electrol%20Bond%20petitions%20involving%20the%20very%20existence%2C%20and%20fairness%20of%20the%20electrol%20process.%20Chief%20Justices%20came%20and%20Chief%20Justices%20went%20away%2C%20each%20shying%20away%20from%20taking%20up%20the%20issue%20head%20on.%20To%20be%20fair%20to%20the%20then%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%2C%20even%20in%20the%20height%20of%20emergency%2C%20when%20Smt.%20Indra%20Gandhi%20reigned%20Supreme%2C%20he%20did%20not%20shy%20away%20from%20constituting%20a%20Bench%20and%20taking%20up%20the%20matter%20of%20%3Cem%3EADM%20Jabalpur%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20is%20a%20different%20matter%20that%20its%20outcome%20was%20highly%20damning%20to%20the%20fundamental%20rights%20of%20the%20citizen%2C%20and%20it%20remains%20an%20ugly%20spot%20on%20the%20fair%20face%20of%20the%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20no%20urgency%20was%20felt%20or%20realised%20by%20one%20Chief%20Justice%20after%20another%20in%20the%20Electoral%20Bonds%20cases%20or%20others%20similar%20matters%20involving%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20citizens%3F%20In%20the%20interregnum%2C%20much%20water%20has%20already%20flown%20under%20the%20bridge.%20One%20general%20election%2C%20and%20many%20elections%20to%20the%20State%20Legislatures%2C%20had%20taken%20place%20in%20the%20meanwhile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20imagine%2C%20when%20a%20judgement%20like%20in%20the%20Electoral%20Bonds%20matter%20comes%20protecting%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20citizens%2C%20they%20are%20not%20only%20pleasantly%20surprised%2C%20but%20feel%20so%20relieved%20as%20to%20hail%20and%20thank%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20even%20when%20it%20has%20only%20performed%20its%20constitutional%20duty.%20And%20when%20it%20does%20that%2C%20it%20neither%20needs%20applause%20nor%20brickbats.%20But%20the%20fact%20that%20such%20was%20the%20reaction%20shows%20how%20much%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20lost%20in%20terms%20of%20credibility%20in%20the%20field%20of%20justice%20delivery%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20no%20longer%20taken%20as%20the%20last%20word%20on%20any%20such%20pronouncement.%20It%20is%20already%20being%20said%20that%20the%20government%20may%20move%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20review%2C%20or%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20and%20the%20Election%20Commission%20may%20ask%20for%20further%20time%20to%20carry%20out%20its%20directions%2C%20or%20the%20government%20may%20even%20bring%20an%20Ordinance%20to%20nullify%20the%20effect%20of%20the%20judgement.%20After%20all%2C%20the%20government%20did%20bring%20an%20Ordinance%20to%20reverse%20the%20judgement%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20selection%20of%20the%20Election%20Commissioners%20by%20removing%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20as%20being%20part%20of%20such%20selection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20have%20things%20come%20to%20such%20a%20pass%3F%20The%20government%20is%20not%20entirely%20to%20be%20blamed.%20Somewhere%20down%20the%20line%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20allowed%20its%20authority%20to%20dilute.%20Though%20it%20is%20unfortunate%2C%20keeping%20in%20view%20the%20past%20performance%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20one%20feels%2C%20it%20is%20the%20government%20which%20will%20have%20the%20last%20laugh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20me%20take%20you%20to%20the%20past.%20The%20aggrieved%20citizen%20was%20known%20by%20the%20name%20of%20Maneka%20Gandhi.%20Our%20Supreme%20Court%20said%2C%20and%20I%20quote%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9Cspeedy%20trial%20is%20a%20dynamic%20and%20progressive%20program%20of%20legal%20assistance%2C%20an%20essential%20ingredient%20of%20the%20right%20to%20life%20and%20liberty%20and%20flows%20directly%20from%20Article%2021%20of%20the%20Constitution%E2%80%9D.%20Brave%20words%2C%20but%20lost%20somewhere%20in%20the%20wilderness%20of%20the%20Roster%20regime.%20You%20do%20not%20live%20on%20words%20alone.%20They%20need%20a%20heart.%20And%20a%20heart%20that%20flutters.%20Thousands%20and%20thousands%20are%20rotting%20in%20jails%2C%20standing%20in%20the%20corridors%20of%20courts%20of%20justice%2C%20day%20in%20and%20day%20out%2C%20with%20prayers%20on%20their%20lips%2C%20hoping%20for%20the%20rule%2C%20%E2%80%9CBail%20not%20Jail%E2%80%9Dto%20resurrect.%20But%20it%20surfaces%20only%20for%20the%20chosen%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddique%20Kappan%2C%20a%20journalist%20who%20was%20arrested%20on%20October%205%2C%202020%2C%20got%20bail%20after%20more%20than%20two%20years.%20When%20he%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20under%20Article%2032%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20then%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20remarked%20that%20we%20want%20to%20discourage%20Article%2032%20petitions%2C%20and%20he%20was%20sent%20back%20to%20the%20High%20Court.%20More%20recently%2C%20Supreme%20Court%20declined%20to%20hear%20an%20Article%2032%20petition%20involving%20the%20arrest%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20a%20State%20who%20alleged%20that%20he%20was%20arrested%20on%20no%20evidence%2C%20and%20with%20the%20sole%20aim%20of%20destabilising%20his%20duly%20elected%20government.%20The%20Bench%20observed%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwhy%20have%20you%20come%20here%20directly%E2%80%9D.%20This%20observation%20was%20made%20notwithstanding%20the%20fact%20that%20many%20a%20times%20in%20the%20past%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20been%20entertaining%20Article%2032%20petitions%20depending%20upon%20the%20urgency%20and%20gravity%20of%20the%20matter.%20And%2C%20more%20importantly%2C%20the%20observation%20has%20come%20notwithstanding%20the%20golden%20words%20of%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%2C%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20describing%20Article%2032%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cheart%20and%20soul%20of%20the%20Constitution%E2%80%9D.%20Is%20Article%2032%20to%20be%20treated%20as%20a%20dead%20letter%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemember%20the%20landmark%20judgement%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F1373215%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHussanara%20Khatoon%20vs.%20State%20of%20Bihar%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20Recollect%20what%20the%20judges%20said%3F%20Let%20me%20remind%20you.%20They%20not%20only%20felt%20that%20there%20was%20a%20shocking%20state%20of%20affairs%20so%20far%20as%20the%20administration%20of%20law%20and%20order%20is%20concerned%2C%20but%20also%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20legal%20system%20has%20lost%20its%20credibility%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArun%20Shourie%20has%20beautifully%20described%20the%20present%20state%20of%20judiciary%20in%20his%20remarkably%20readable%20book%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Commission%20for%20Lost%20Causes%3C%2Fem%3E.%20He%20calls%20the%20judges%20as%20%E2%80%9CLions%20under%20the%20throne%E2%80%9D.%20The%20misfortune%20is%20that%20many%20of%20them%20have%20not%20only%20lost%20their%20teeth%20but%20roar%20too%2C%20leaving%20the%20ordinary%20citizen%20to%20the%20mercy%20of%20predators%20and%20jackals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20we%20find%20today%20is%20that%20while%20a%20powerful%20person%20gets%20bail%20on%20an%20experimental%20basis%2C%20men%20like%20Umar%20Khalid%20are%20withering%20away%2C%20unwept%2C%20unsung%20and%20unheard%2C%20and%20so%20fed%20up%20that%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20corridors%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20itself%20considered%20a%20relief.%20While%20a%20journalist%20spends%20time%20in%20jail%20for%20the%20mere%20crime%20of%20performing%20his%20duty%2C%20an%20old%20and%20ailing%20man%20unable%20to%20even%20sip%20water%20is%20denied%20basic%20medical%20aid%2C%20and%20is%20made%20to%20suffer%20and%20die%20behind%20the%20bars.%20What%20has%20happened%20to%20Article%2021%3F%20Why%20have%20those%20swearing%20by%20the%20Constitution%20forgotten%20cases%20like%20Hussainara%2C%20M.H.%20Hoskot%2C%20Sunil%20Batra%20and%20A.K.%20Roy%3F%20What%20has%20happened%20to%20those%20brave%20words%20in%3Cem%3E%20Rattan%20Singh%20versus%20State%20of%20Punja%3C%2Fem%3Eb%20(AIR%201982%20Supreme%20Court%201)%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6If%20freedom%20and%20liberty%20are%20to%20have%20any%20meaning%20in%20our%20democratic%20setup%2C%20it%20is%20essential%20that%20at%20least%20those%20safeguards%20are%20not%20denied.%E2%80%9D%20Is%20our%20judiciary%20pushing%20down%20who%20deserve%20to%20be%20pushed%20down%20and%20pulling%20up%20who%20deserve%20to%20be%20pulled%20up%2C%20or%20is%20it%20just%20becoming%20gilded%20tomb%20of%20a%20failed%20talent%3F%20The%20question%20is%20not%20who%20is%20making%20them%20dance.%20The%20question%20is%20who%20is%20dancing%20and%20why%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20was%20penning%20these%20lines%2C%20I%20had%20before%20me%20two%20headlines%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Without%20a%20comment%2C%20I%20am%20reading%20them%20out%20to%20you%2C%20leaving%20it%20to%20you%20to%20react.%20Here%20is%20the%20first%20one.%20A%20Bench%20of%20Justice%20B.R.%20Gavai%20and%20Sandeep%20Mehta%20observed%20%E2%80%9Cwhen%20the%20question%20of%20liberty%20of%20a%20person%20is%20involved%2C%20even%20a%C2%A0day%E2%80%99s%20delay%20counts%E2%80%9D%20(January%2018%2C%202024)%20and%20here%20is%20the%20second%20one%2C%20%E2%80%9C24%20years%20after%20a%20man%20dies%20in%20police%20custody%2C%20ex-cop%20sentenced%20to%2010%20years%20jail%E2%80%9D.%20How%20do%20you%20reconcile%20the%20two%3F%20One%20decries%20even%20a%20day%E2%80%99s%20delay%20and%20the%20other%20tells%20us%20of%20delay%20of%2024%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemember%20those%20five%20judges%20of%20the%20press%20conference%20fame.%20One%20of%20them%2C%20a%20friend%20from%20days%20of%20our%20mutual%20struggle%20at%20the%20Bar%2C%20is%20present%20today.%20What%20happened%20thereafter%3F%20Any%20reform%3F%20Any%20improvement%3F%20Let%20us%20remember%20that%20a%20driver%E2%80%99s%20competence%20is%20not%20established%20by%20his%20dress%20or%20his%20religious%20fervor%20made%20public%2C%20but%20by%20making%20his%20passengers%20reach%20their%20destination%20safely.%20A%20judge%20must%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20the%20Constitution%20before%20he%20approaches%20it.%20The%20original%20is%20beautiful.%20Its%20reach%20is%20not%20limited.%20It%20is%20not%20the%20Roster%2C%20it%20is%20the%20judge%20who%20assigns%20the%20cases%2C%20and%20it%20is%20the%20judge%20who%20decides%20the%20matter.%3Cbr%3E%5CnShakespeare%20in%20Julius%20Caesar%20writes%3A%20%E2%80%9CHis%20life%20was%20gentle%2C%20and%20the%20elements%20so%20mixed%20in%20him%20that%20Nature%20might%20stand-up.%20And%20say%20to%20all%20the%20world.%20This%20was%20a%20man.%E2%80%9D%20Are%20we%20today%20too%20sure%20of%20the%20presence%20of%20such%20a%20man%3F%20If%20not%2C%20surely%2C%20we%20need%20him%2C%20though%20many%20today%20are%20seen%20taking%20a%20deep%20breath%20and%20agreeing%20with%20Meer%20Taqi%20Meer%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EIbtadaai%20ishq%20hai%2C%20rota%20hai%20kya%20agey%20agey%20dekhiye%20hota%20hai%20kya.%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20having%20said%20all%20this%2C%20I%20will%20be%20unfair%20to%20the%20Roster%20System%2C%20and%20to%20its%20Master%2C%20by%20not%20pointing%20out%20at%20least%20three%20pronounced%20advantages%20of%20the%20Roster%20System%20and%20which%2C%20fortunately%20or%20unfortunately%2C%20have%20already%20become%20public%20and%2C%20they%20are%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20The%20Master%20of%20Roster%20can%20constitute%20a%20Bench%20of%20his%20own%20choice%20and%20himself%20preside%20over%20it%20even%20in%20a%20very%20personal%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20By%20intelligently%20making%20use%20of%20that%20power%2C%20he%20can%20assure%20himself%2C%20even%20after%20his%20retirement%2C%20a%20cozy%20job%20like%20a%20seat%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20or%20Governorship%20in%20some%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20By%20intelligently%20using%20that%20power%2C%20he%20can%20equally%20benefit%20his%20very%20worthy%20and%20dearest%20colleagues%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThank%20you%20very%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708863927000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25222448%2FSupreme-Court-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fthe-supreme-court-has-allowed-its-authority-to-be-diluted%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20a%20seminar%20organised%20by%20the%20Campaign%20for%20Judicial%20Accountability%20and%20Reforms%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20The%20Wire%20and%20LiveLaw%2C%20Justice%20Rekha%20Sharma%20discussed%20why%20the%20present%20state%20of%20affairs%20in%20the%20court%20needs%20remedy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fthe-supreme-court-has-allowed-its-authority-to-be-diluted%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RLD-BJP%20Alliance%3A%20What%20Does%20the%20Changed%20Political%20Equations%20Now%20Hold%20for%20Western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23172343%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-23-at-5.22.55-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMuzaffarnagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20motorcycle%20rally%20led%20by%20the%20BJP%20passes%20through%20sugarcane%20fields%20in%20Budhana%2C%20Muzaffarnagar.%20The%20bikes%20are%20decorated%20with%20flags%20of%20the%20saffron%20party%20while%20a%20song%20plays%20in%20the%20background%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Mazdoor%20kisan%20ke%20haq%20mein%20ye%20alakh%20jagai%20re%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3ERLD%20aayi%20re%2C%20RLD%20aayi%20re%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98(This%20awakening%20is%20happening%20in%20support%20of%20labourers%20and%20farmers%2C%20RLD%20%5BRashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%5D%20has%20come%2C%20RLD%20has%20come).%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20sugarcane%20plots%20belong%20to%20Shobhan%20Singh%2C%2080%20who%20has%20seen%20the%20influence%20of%20the%20former%20prime%20minister%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20politics.%20A%20%3Cem%3Echaupal%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20been%20set%20up%2C%20at%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20fields%2C%20where%20he%20sits%20with%20a%20hookah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20his%20thoughts%2C%20Shobhan%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CChaudhary%20Sahib%20deserved%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20but%20no%20past%20prime%20minister%20thought%20of%20honouring%20him%20in%20this%20manner.%20Now%20it%20is%20natural%20for%20Chaudhary%20Sahib%E2%80%99s%20grandson%20Jayant%20to%20lean%20towards%20the%20BJP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20villagers%20nod%20in%20agreement%2C%20puffing%20on%20their%20hookahs%2C%20wondering%20aloud%20farmer%20Shivam%20Choudhary%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EDadda%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20do%20you%20think%20that%20Bharat%20Ratna%20alone%20made%20Jayant%20Choudhary%20distance%20himself%20from%20the%20INDIA%20Alliance%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERLD%E2%80%99s%20prospects%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERLD%20chief%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%20who%20is%20known%20for%20his%20staunch%20opposition%20to%20the%20BJP%20truly%20shocked%20everyone%20by%20parting%20ways%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20and%20switching%20loyalties%20to%20the%20NDA%20within%20hours%20of%20Bharat%20Ratna%20award%20announcement%20for%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20on%20February%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENext%20day%2C%20while%20speaking%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20a%20turncoat%20Jayant%20said%20aloud%2C%20%E2%80%9CHaving%20been%20in%20the%20opposition%20for%2010%20years%2C%20I%20see%20shades%20of%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20ideology%20in%20the%20present%20government%E2%80%99s%20working%20style.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20towering%20figure%20in%20farmer%20politics%2C%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20had%20devised%20a%20caste%20coalition%20formula%20then%20popularly%20known%20%E2%80%98MAJGAR%E2%80%99%20(Muslim%2C%20Ahir%2C%20Jat%2C%20Gujjar%2C%20and%20Rajput%20communities)%20which%20contributed%20significantly%20to%20his%20success%20in%20the%20western%20part%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffor-bharat-ratna-chaudhary-charan-singh-politics-meant-the-art-of-possible%5C%22%3EFor%20%E2%80%98Bharat%20Ratna%E2%80%99%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20Politics%20Meant%20the%20Art%20of%20the%20Possible%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20was%20a%20grassroots%20leader%2C%20representing%20farmers%20of%20all%20castes.%20However%2C%20after%20his%20passing%20away%2C%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20diminished%2C%20narrowing%20down%20to%20primarily%20representing%20the%20Jat%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20senior%20journalist%20Brijesh%20Shukla.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20party%E2%80%99s%20downfall%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20its%20tendency%20to%20align%20with%20larger%20parties%20like%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%2C%20rather%20than%20focusing%20on%20strengthening%20its%20own%20foundation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%202014%20elections%2C%20even%20the%20Jat%20support%20base%20of%20the%20RLD%20began%20to%20dwindle%20particularly%20on%20account%20of%20the%20divide%20between%20Muslims%20and%20Jats%20essentially%20following%20the%20infamous%202013%20Muzaffarnagar%20riots%20which%20left%20more%20than%2065%20people%20dead%20and%20thousands%20displaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20CSDS%20post-poll%20studies%20on%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20garnered%2077%25%20of%20the%20Jat%20votes%2C%20a%20stark%20increase%20from%20the%207%25%20it%20received%20in%20the%202012%20Assembly%20elections.%20In%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20there%20was%20a%20considerable%20anticipation%20as%20an%20ambitious%20grand%20alliance%20of%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%2C%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%2C%20and%20RLD%20was%20formed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Muslims%2C%20Jats%20and%20Dalits%20comprising%20approximately%2060%25%20of%20the%20voting%20population%20in%20Western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20RLD%20harboured%20high%20hopes.%20However%2C%20when%20the%20results%20were%20announced%2C%20it%20sent%20shockwaves%20as%20both%20Ajit%20Singh%20and%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%20lost%20their%20seats%20once%20again%2C%20with%20the%20RLD%20failing%20to%20even%20open%20its%20account%20and%20the%20BJP%20took%20away%2091%25%20of%20the%20Jat%20vote%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202022%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Assembly%20election%2C%20unfolded%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20massive%20farmer%20protests%20in%20the%20western%20region%20that%20had%20been%20ongoing%20for%20months.%20The%20RLD%20then%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20SP%20hoped%20to%20bridge%20the%20gap%20between%20Muslims%20and%20Jats.%20However%2C%20the%20results%20remained%20shocking%20for%20RLD%20which%20failed%20to%20win%20more%20than%208%20of%20the%2033%20seats%20it%20contested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrijesh%20Shukla%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20RLD%20failed%20to%20secure%20victory%20despite%20being%20part%20of%20the%20grand%20alliance%20in%202019%20or%20amidst%20extensive%20farmer%20protests%20in%202022%2C%20when%20the%20odds%20were%20stacked%20against%20the%20BJP%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20difficult%20to%20see%20how%20they%20could%20emerge%20victorious%20in%202024.%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%20was%20already%20fighting%20a%20losing%20battle.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJayant%20Choudhary%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20join%20the%20NDA%20alliance%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20notable%20advantage%20for%20the%20RLD%2C%20signalling%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20party%20securing%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20prospect%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20village%20of%20Firozpur%20Bangar%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Adityanath%20is%20seen%20engaging%20with%20villagers%20during%20a%20%3Cem%3Echaupal%3C%2Fem%3E%20session%2C%20where%20he%20acquaints%20them%20with%20various%20beneficiary%20schemes%20initiated%20by%20the%20central%20and%20state%20governments.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20launches%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Gram%20Parikrama%20Yatra%20in%20the%20state%2C%20slated%20to%20cover%2050%2C000%20villages%20across%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Following%20the%20%3Cem%3Echaupal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20while%20addressing%20villagers%20in%20a%20rally%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFarmers%20have%20always%20greeted%20each%20other%20with%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ERam%20Ram%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ERam%20Ram%20Sa%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ERam%20Ramji%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99.%20With%20the%20divine%20arrival%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20on%20one%20hand%20and%20the%20recognition%20of%20the%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20leader%2C%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20with%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20on%20the%20other%2C%20I%20urge%20our%20farmers%20to%20convey%20their%20felicitations%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20speech%20sheds%20light%20on%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20in%20the%20region%2C%20highlighting%20four%20major%20issues%20the%20party%20is%20focusing%20in%20Western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3A%20hindutva%2C%20utilising%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20to%20woo%20Jayant%20and%20farmers%2C%20beneficiary%20schemes%2C%20and%20capitalising%20on%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShamshad%20Khan%2C%20psephologist%20and%20managing%20director%20of%20the%C2%A0PEACS%C2%A0news%20service%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CChaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20commands%20immense%20respect%20in%20the%20region.%20By%20awarding%20him%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%2C%20the%20BJP%20aims%20to%20accomplish%20two%20objectives%3A%20building%20goodwill%20among%20farmers%20and%20drawing%20RLD%20into%20their%20camp%2C%20thereby%20dealing%20a%20significant%20psychological%20blow%20to%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20and%20SP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Futtar-pradeshs-economy-down-the-rabbit-hole-and-beyond%5C%22%3EUttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Economy%3A%20Down%20the%20Rabbit%20Hole%20and%20Beyond%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%20the%20BJP%20is%20also%20working%20to%20get%20its%20caste%20equation%20right%20in%20the%20region.%20Laxmi%20Kant%20Bajpai%2C%20BJP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Meerut%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CNot%20only%20Jats%2C%20but%20we%20have%20also%20actively%20connected%20with%20numerically%20smaller%20communities%20in%20the%20region%2C%20such%20as%20Tyagis%2C%20Sainis%2C%20Gujjars%2C%20Lohaars%2C%20Kahaars%2C%20and%20Kanchis.%20Moreover%2C%20our%20various%20beneficiary%20schemes%20have%20significantly%20benefited%20these%20groups%2C%20and%20we%20expect%20even%20stronger%20support%20from%20them%20in%20the%20upcoming%20election.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20BSP%20steadily%20losing%20its%20hold%20over%20its%20Dalit%20base%2C%20all%20political%20rivals%20are%20out%20to%20grab%20whatever%20they%20can%20out%20of%20the%20Dalit%20vote.%20And%20BJP%20appears%20to%20be%20way%20ahead%20of%20others%2C%20having%20already%20secured%20a%20substantial%20portion%20of%20Dalit%20voters%20from%20the%20BSP%2C%20the%20party%20is%20continuing%20its%20efforts%20to%20expand%20its%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23172719%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-23-at-5.25.31-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22864%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23172719%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-23-at-5.25.31-PM.png%20864w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23172719%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-23-at-5.25.31-PM-300x208.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698557%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22599%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBJP%20leader%20Asim%20Arun%20during%20a%20campaign%20trail.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40asim_arun%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20has%20made%20substantial%20efforts%20toward%20the%20upliftment%20of%20SC%20and%20ST%20communities.%20Not%20only%20have%20our%20welfare%20schemes%20greatly%20benefited%20these%20communities%20but%20the%20BJP%20has%20also%20paid%20homage%20to%20icons%20like%20Baba%20Saheb%20Bhimrao%20Ambedkar%20and%20Birsa%20Munda%2C%20instilling%20confidence%20that%20Modi%3Cem%3E%20ji%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20will%20continue%20to%20empower%20every%20downtrodden%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Asim%20Arun%2C%20former%20police%20commissioner%20of%20Kanpur%20and%20now%20minist