usted%20him.%20They%20did%20not%20make%20him%20do%20menial%20work.%20The%20air%20strike%20happened%20when%20the%20trench%20was%20being%20dug%20up.%20A%20Nepalese%20was%20also%20among%20those%20killed%2C%E2%80%9D%20another%20Indian%20worker%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20paper%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20email%20sent%20on%20behalf%20of%20Mangukiya%E2%80%99s%20father%20to%20the%20Indian%20consulate%20on%20February%202%20urged%20the%20government%20to%20arrange%20for%20his%20son%E2%80%99s%20return%20citing%20the%20risk%20to%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20on%20Friday%20said%20that%20it%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fgovt-in-talks-with-russian-authorities-for-early-discharge-of-indians-forced-to-fight-in-russia%5C%22%3Eapproached%20Russian%20authorities%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Cearly%20discharge%E2%80%9D%20of%20Indians%20working%20with%20the%20Russian%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20nationals%20who%20had%20come%20forward%20alleging%20mistreatment%20said%20that%20their%20pleas%20for%20help%20from%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20in%20Moscow%20had%20gone%20unheard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhmad%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fgujarati-security-helper-in-russian-army-killed-in-ukrainian-air-strike%2Farticle67882488.ece%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20came%20together%20from%20India.%20Hemil%20died%20in%20front%20of%20me.%20We%20fear%20that%20they%20may%20send%20us%20to%20the%20border%20and%20we%20will%20also%20be%20left%20to%20die.%20When%20we%20ask%20the%20Russian%20commander%20to%20relieve%20us%2C%20he%20said%20we%20have%20signed%20a%20contract.%20The%20commander%20said%20we%20will%20get%20Hemil%E2%80%99s%20body%20after%20two%20months.%20Please%20save%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20worker%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20paper%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20hired%20as%20army%20security%20helpers%20but%20they%20are%20forcing%20us%20to%20f