ticles%2Fs41586-020-3010-5.epdf%3Fsharing_token%3D3CHo0xfe3Tvd1YG75jq_pNRgN0jAjWel9jnR3ZoTv0MLvUZ1C0L35yEQYHf_pwmiKx-xqIzWDg-_bH8WmUJdQjqDv1hJIWjUwOgpVde7Oc47mU9HfjoCpd8F0qewoXmjl6QNLlUMD2eeD21ompdgtw3j2FQ9z0hhBzCsqewC9BUQNhgBo5rYNFnTf9gTg419kTld3VXUhXOFlygv007wkcA8jVVlyrBd14KL3O0lNyBuKzwyEi3JweVEIQx-q--iJqnayOdwj9gTpRTWTtTOJvoFaa4lpPQmXm028aQBnHeATCYjwcYRKdCqhVNLeXvQ7j3y2D0Sgl2n5GZ2dTzvvg%3D%3D%26tracking_referrer%3Dwww.theguardian.com%26mbid%3D%26utm_source%3Dnl%26utm_brand%3Dtny%26utm_mailing%3DTNY_ClimateCrisis_121620%26utm_campaign%3Daud-dev%26utm_medium%3Demail%26bxid%3D5bea135b2ddf9c72dc90b66f%26cndid%3D45440288%26hasha%3Deb414f952806f05d6e7ff11d39c89797%26hashb%3Ddb3a5a1e0a396f85c747577a7ee7ea5f22c3f952%26hashc%3Dab4d7c2deb32c71870617a467ead721a55e73fca010ec22a21b4db12fe04792c%26esrc%3Dno_source_code%26utm_term%3DTNY_ClimateCrisis%5C%22%3Eartificial%20materials%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20continuously%20produced%20at%20an%20amount%20equivalent%20to%20the%20total%20body%20mass%20of%20all%20living%20people.%20This%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20even%20include%20our%20industrial%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndustrial%20capitalist%20society%20is%20built%20upon%20this%20production%20of%20surplus%20food%2C%20materials%2C%20and%20extra-somatic%20energy%20for%20use%20by%20some%20humans%20more%20than%20others.%20It%20blithely%20presumes%20that%20the%20ecosphere%20will%20readily%20provide%20the%20energy%20and%20materials%20to%20fuel%20this%20overconsumption%20and%20then%20absorb%20the%20mountains%20and%20rivers%20and%20islands%20of%20concomitant%20waste%20and%20pollution%E2%80%94including%20all%20the%20excess%20carbon%20dioxide%20we%20emit.%20The%20cost%20of%20this%20is%E2%80%94as%20it%20has%20always%20been%E2%80%94the%20destruction%20of%20the%20local%20ecosystem%2C%20which%20today%20encompasses%20the%20whole%20planet%2C%20thus%20driving%20the%20mass%20extinction%20of%20non-human%20species%20and%20the%20destruction%20of%20many%20human%20groups%20as%20well.%20The%20result%20is%20a%20biosphere%20critically%20lacking%20in%20biodiversity%2C%20frightfully%20over-polluted%2C%20morbidly%20out%20of%20balance%20and%20overwhelmed%20by%20the%20over-population%20of%20its%20apex%20predator%20species%3A%20humans.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stockholmresilience.org%2F5.3d04209a18a2642b2fc162a3.html%5C%22%3Eexceeded%20six%20of%20the%20nine%3C%2Fa%3E%20known%20planetary%20boundaries%20for%20civilizational%20stability.%20Today%20our%20species%20is%20in%20a%20perilous%20state%20of%20ecological%20overshoot.%20Climate%20change%20is%20merely%20one%20symptom%20of%20this%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20strangling%20the%20web%20of%20life%2C%20triggering%20an%20extinction%20event%20such%20as%20our%20planet%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20witnessed%20since%20the%20age%20of%20the%20dinosaurs.%20We%20might%20glean%20from%20this%20the%20same%20fundamental%20lesson%20our%20ancient%20ancestors%20would%20have%20heeded%2C%20when%20they%20were%20not%20so%20separated%20from%20the%20ecological%20feedbacks%20of%20their%20actions.%20Indeed%2C%20some%20communities%20around%20the%20world%20who%20still%20follow%20lifestyles%20much%20more%20closely%20connected%20with%20the%20land%20have%20seen%20the%20signs%20of%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pnas.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1073%2Fpnas.142033699%5C%22%3Eecological%20overshoot%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20have%20tried%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTq0kWs1q3hI%5C%22%3Ewarn%20us%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpwccc.wordpress.com%2Fsupport%2F%5C%22%3Erepeatedly%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20was%20it%20that%20prompted%20such%20a%20dramatic%20change%20in%20the%20way%20so%20many%20people%20chose%20to%20live%2C%20to%20shift%20from%20immediate-return%20to%20delayed-return%20economies%3F%20From%20socially%20egalitarian%2C%20decentralized%2C%20diverse%20and%20fluidly%20inter-linked%20communities%20to%20deeply%20stratified%2C%20centralized%2C%20relatively%20homogeneous%20and%20bounded%20nation-states%3F%20When%20did%20it%20all%20begin%20to%20change%3F%20Why%3F%20And%20as%20a%20species%2C%20why%20are%20we%20not%20(yet)%20suffering%20population%20decline%20when%20we%20so%20utterly%20despoil%20our%20environment%2C%20as%20our%20ancestors%20suffered%20if%20they%20ruined%20theirs%3F%20The%20answers%20may%20not%20be%20what%20most%20of%20us%20are%20led%20to%20presume.%20I%20will%20attempt%20to%20tease%20them%20out%20in%20the%20forthcoming%20essays%20of%20this%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EUsha%20Alexander%20trained%20in%20science%20and%20anthropology.%20After%20working%20for%20years%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20she%20now%20lives%20in%20Gurugram.%20She%E2%80%99s%20written%20two%20novels%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Legend%20of%20Virinara%3Cem%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EOnly%20the%20Eyes%20Are%20Mine%3Cem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708843504000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25113632%2FIMG_2939.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fthe-human-animal-in-the-circle-of-life%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Energy%20and%20materials%20flow%20through%20this%20circle%20of%20life%E2%80%94really%2C%20multiple%20interconnected%20circles%2C%20or%20a%20web%20of%20life%E2%80%94with%20each%20species%20occupying%20its%20place%2C%20or%20niche%2C%20within%20the%20flow.%20But%20now%2C%20humans%20are%20strangling%20the%20web%20of%20life%2C%20triggering%20an%20extinction%20event%20such%20as%20our%20planet%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20witnessed%20since%20the%20age%20of%20the%20dinosaurs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fthe-human-animal-in-the-circle-of-life%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22900%20Kids%20Are%20Now%20Able%20to%20Hear%2C%20Thanks%20to%20Support%20From%20This%20Life-Changing%20Initiative%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20child%20is%20born%2C%20parents%20celebrate%20each%20milestone%20in%20their%20life%20%E2%80%94%20from%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20first%20rollover%20to%20crawling%20and%20walking.%20Another%20significant%20moment%20every%20parent%20eagerly%20awaits%20is%20their%20baby%E2%80%99s%20first%20word.%20Each%20child%20develops%20uniquely%2C%20hitting%20these%20milestones%20at%20different%20times.%20However%2C%20parents%20need%20to%20remain%20attentive%20and%20raise%20concerns%20if%20these%20milestones%20are%20delayed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334578%2Fcoda-child-of-deaf-adult-indian-sign-language-isl%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHearing%2C%20an%20invisible%20aspect%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20often%20goes%20unnoticed%20until%20the%20child%20begins%20to%20speak%20or%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t.%20A%20child%20who%20is%20not%20able%20to%20hear%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20able%20to%20respond%20to%20noises%20or%20their%20name%2C%20and%20won%E2%80%99t%20start%20babbling%20and%20trying%20to%20imitate%20sounds%20by%20six%20to%20eight%20months.%20If%20parents%20are%20not%20aware%20of%20such%20childhood%20milestones%20they%20may%20not%20become%20aware%20of%20potential%20hearing%20issues%20until%20around%20the%20time%20the%20child%20reaches%20two%20years%20of%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20advancements%20in%20healthcare%20and%20technology%2C%20newborn%20hearing%20screenings%20can%20now%20detect%20hearing%20loss%20much%20before%20even%20the%20earliest%20milestones-based%20diagnosis.%20These%20screenings%20aid%20in%20the%20early%20detection%20of%20hearing%20problems%2C%20allowing%20for%20follow-up%20consultations%20with%20paediatricians%20within%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20first%20two%20to%20three%20months%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20estimates%20that%20there%20are%2063%20million%20people%20in%20India%20who%20suffer%20from%20significant%20auditory%20impairment.%20It%20further%20notes%20that%20up%20to%20five%20out%20of%20every%201%2C000%20babies%20are%20born%20with%20hearing%20loss%20or%20acquire%20it%20soon%20after%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20key%20to%20effective%20management%20of%20hearing%20loss%20is%20early%20identification%20and%20prompt%20treatment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChildren%20experiencing%20mild%20to%20moderate%20hearing%20loss%20can%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F63445%2Fhearing-impairments-balavidyalaya-school-chennai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebenefit%20from%20hearing%20aids%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20those%20with%20profound%20hearing%20loss%2C%20Cochlear%20Implants%20(CI)%20offer%20a%20solution.%20These%20electronic%20devices%20serve%20to%20replace%20the%20function%20of%20the%20damaged%20inner%20ear%2C%20facilitating%20the%20sense%20of%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20enables%20children%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20auditory%20world%20and%20lead%20lives%20similar%20to%20other%20children%20in%20every%20aspect.%20However%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20Cochlear%20Implant%20(CI)%20surgery%20is%20expensive%20for%20a%20large%20portion%20of%20the%20population%20in%20India.%20To%20assist%20children%20in%20regaining%20their%20hearing%20abilities%20and%20leading%20fulfilling%20lives%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341889%2Fhans-foundation-bal-aarogya-karyakram-childhood-cancer-paediatric-oncology-leukaemia-lymphoma%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Hans%20Foundation%20%3C%2Fa%3E(THF)%20runs%20the%20Cochlear%20Implant%20Programme.%20Through%20this%20initiative%2C%20they%20have%20already%20helped%20over%20900%20children%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20two-hour%20surgery%20that%20can%20change%20lives%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_1342-min-1708783870-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Hans%20Foundation%20(THF)%20has%20helped%20over%20900%20children%20with%20its%20Cochlear%20Implant%20Programme.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_1342-min-1708783870-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_1342-min-1708783870-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_1342-min-1708783870-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_1342-min-1708783870-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_1342-min-1708783870-1536x1152.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_1342-min-1708783870-2048x1536.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_1342-min-1708783870-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343117%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Hans%20Foundation%20(THF)%20has%20helped%20over%20900%20children%20with%20its%20Cochlear%20Implant%20Programme%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhen%20Sukhjot%20Kaur%20turned%20two%2C%20her%20parents%20started%20worrying%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20she%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20uttered%20her%20first%20word.%20The%20elders%20in%20the%20house%20told%20the%20concerned%20parents%20not%20to%20worry%20as%20everyone%20in%20their%20family%20had%20started%20speaking%20late.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20an%20alert%20neighbour%20who%20helped%20Sukhjot%E2%80%99s%20parents%20identify%20her%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20toddler%20was%20playing%20outside%20her%20house%20in%20Delhi%2C%20a%20passing%20car%20honked%20many%20times%20but%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%20move.%20The%20neighbour%20who%20noticed%20this%20immediately%20told%20Sukhjot%E2%80%99s%20mother%2C%20Rajinder%20Kaur%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20your%20daughter%20can%20hear.%20Take%20her%20to%20the%20doctor!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajinder%20hurriedly%20took%20her%20two-and-a-half-year-old%20daughter%20to%20a%20hospital%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20where%20the%20doctor%20diagnosed%20her%20with%20severe%20hearing%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20went%20to%20many%20hospitals%20after%20that%2C%20including%20AIIMS.%20Everyone%20gave%20the%20same%20diagnosis.%20They%20said%20that%20we%20needed%20to%20get%20a%20cochlear%20implant%2C%20which%20would%20cost%20almost%20Rs%206%20to%207%20lakh.%20My%20husband%20is%20an%20auto%20driver%20and%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20fathom%20how%20to%20cough%20up%20such%20a%20big%20amount%20of%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rajinder%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYears%20passed%20as%20the%20couple%20visited%20various%20hospitals%20and%20explored%20different%20options.%20In%202014%2C%20when%20the%20child%20was%20five%20years%20old%2C%20they%20were%20introduced%20to%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%2C%20which%20offered%20assistance.%20With%20their%20financial%20support%2C%20Sukhjot%20received%20a%20cochlear%20implant%20that%20year%20and%20is%20now%20flourishing%20in%20a%20mainstream%20school%20just%20like%20any%20other%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20daughter%20can%20now%20speak%20well%20and%20is%20a%20good%20student.%20She%20also%20paints%20very%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Rajinder%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20yearning%20to%20hear%20her%20speak.%20Now%2C%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20have%20enough%20of%20it!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1708783652.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sukhjot%20received%20a%20cochlear%20implant%20and%20is%20now%20flourishing%20in%20school%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1708783652.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1708783652-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1708783652-500x281.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1708783652-768x432.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1708783652-150x84.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343113%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESukhjot%20received%20a%20cochlear%20implant%20and%20is%20now%20flourishing%20in%20school.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341755%2Fcongenital-heart-disease-in-babies-treatment-surgery-provided-by-hans-foundation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Hans%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fa%3E%20intervention%20has%20supported%20the%20surgeries%20and%20rehabilitation%20of%20over%20900%20children%20across%2014%20hospitals%20in%20seven%20states%2C%20from%20its%20start%20in%20December%202013%20to%20date.%20Dr%20Ravi%20Bhatia%2C%20an%20ENT%20surgeon%20at%20Sarvodaya%20Hospital%20%E2%80%94%20a%20partner%20of%20THF%20%E2%80%94%20explains%20that%20a%20cochlear%20implant%20aids%20children%20with%20severe%20hearing%20loss%20in%20listening%2C%20understanding%2C%20and%20beginning%20to%20speak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20cochlear%20implant%20is%20an%20electronic%20device%20which%20is%20implanted%20through%20surgery%20into%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20ear.%20It%20bypasses%20the%20damaged%20hair%20cells%20of%20the%20inner%20ear%20or%20cochlea%20to%20provide%20sound%20signals%20to%20the%20brain%20by%20stimulating%20the%20inner%20ear%2C%20which%20helps%20the%20child%20to%20start%20hearing.%20There%20is%20an%20internal%20and%20external%20device%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20implant%20comprises%20an%20external%20component%20placed%20behind%20the%20ear%20and%20a%20second%20component%20surgically%20implanted%20under%20the%20skin.%20This%20surgery%20can%20be%20performed%20as%20early%20as%20six%20to%20eight%20months%20of%20age%20and%20ideally%20should%20be%20completed%20by%20the%20time%20the%20child%20reaches%20three%20years%20old%2C%20ensuring%20timely%20access%20to%20schooling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20newborn%20hearing%20screening%2C%20the%20doctors%20can%20assess%20if%20the%20baby%20has%20any%20hearing%20loss.%20Through%20a%20battery%20of%20tests%20and%20follow-ups%2C%20by%20the%20time%20the%20child%20is%20three%20to%20four%20months%20old%2C%20it%20becomes%20clear%20if%20the%20baby%20needs%20a%20cochlear%20implant%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20baby%20reaches%20eight%20months%20old%2C%20they%20are%20ready%20for%20the%20surgery%2C%20which%20typically%20lasts%20two%20and%20a%20half%20hours.%20However%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20note%20that%20the%20surgery%20alone%20addresses%20only%2020%20percent%20of%20the%20problem.%20What%E2%80%99s%20equally%20important%20is%20the%20post-surgery%20Auditory%20Verbal%20Therapy%20(AVT)%2C%20which%20spans%20two%20years%20and%20requires%20parental%20involvement%20to%20ensure%20the%20child%20develops%20spoken%20language%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETHF%20states%20that%20each%20cochlear%20implant%20procedure%20with%20the%20device%2C%20surgery%20and%20rehabilitation%20costs%20about%20Rs%208-9%20lakh%20per%20ear.%20THF%20also%20provides%20support%20for%20this%20therapy%20and%20ensures%20that%20parents%20from%20underprivileged%20backgrounds%20have%20access%20to%20therapists%20and%20can%20continue%20the%20therapy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Don%E2%80%99t%20ignore%20warning%20signs%20of%20hearing%20loss%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-16-1708783874.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cochlear%20implant%20surgery%20is%20most%20effective%20when%20done%20in%20the%200-5%20age%20group%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-16-1708783874.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-16-1708783874-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-16-1708783874-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-16-1708783874-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-16-1708783874-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343118%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECochlear%20implant%20surgery%20is%20most%20effective%20when%20done%20in%20the%200-3%20age%20group%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20in%20Sukhjot%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20many%20parents%20come%20to%20doctors%20late%2C%20says%20Dr%20Bhatia.%20This%20lack%20of%20awareness%20causes%20significant%20delays%20in%20the%20surgery%2C%20affecting%20outcomes.%20An%20internal%20study%20conducted%20by%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20revealed%20that%20hearing%20outcomes%20among%20children%20who%20received%20implants%20between%20the%20ages%20of%20zero%20and%20three%20were%20two%20and%20a%20half%20times%20improved%20compared%20to%20those%20implanted%20at%20ages%20four%20and%20older.%20Hence%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20identify%20and%20undergo%20implantation%20before%20the%20age%20of%20three%20for%20a%20favourable%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20of%20parents%20are%20in%20denial%20about%20their%20children%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F328341%2Fyunikee-empowers-deaf-persons-accessing-hearing-solutions-govt-jobs-skills%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehearing%20loss%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20India.%20Elders%20also%20support%20their%20beliefs%20saying%20that%20even%20we%20spoke%20late.%20When%20a%20child%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20listen%20to%20sounds%20or%20react%20to%20sounds%2C%20parents%20must%20raise%20a%20red%20flag.%20Go%20to%20a%20doctor%20and%20get%20your%20child%20checked%20if%20you%20notice%20anything%20wrong%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Bhatia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20grows%20its%20commitment%20to%20supporting%20several%20life-changing%20medical%20interventions%20for%20children%20from%20underprivileged%20backgrounds%20under%20its%20larger%20umbrella%20of%20Hans%20Paediatric%20Care%2C%20support%20for%20children%20who%20need%20cochlear%20implant%20surgeries%20remains%20a%20key%20part%20of%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETHF%20works%20closely%20with%20its%20hospital%20partners%20for%20these%20surgeries.%20Doctors%20from%20the%20partner%20hospitals%20and%20their%20networks%20identify%20children%20who%20need%20support%20and%20connect%20them%20with%20the%20foundation%E2%80%99s%20programme.%20THF%20ensures%20that%20the%20family%20is%20prepared%20to%20commit%20to%20post-surgery%20therapy%20and%20maintain%20the%20device%20properly.%20Dr%20Bhatia%20emphasises%20the%20importance%20of%20periodic%20battery%20replacements%20and%20regular%20cleaning%20of%20the%20device.%20Additionally%2C%20patients%20should%20take%20precautions%20to%20avoid%20ear%20injuries%20and%20promptly%20seek%20medical%20attention%20in%20case%20of%20infections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20a%20decade%20of%20experience%20with%20the%20programme%2C%20the%20Foundation%20has%20observed%20that%20the%20success%20of%20a%20cochlear%20implant%20is%20based%20on%20a%20multitude%20of%20factors.%20The%20cause%20and%20type%20of%20hearing%20impairment%20have%20an%20effect%2C%20but%20so%20does%20the%20age%20of%20the%20child%2C%20time%20elapsed%20since%20the%20onset%20of%20hearing%20loss%2C%20active%20implant%20use%2C%20and%20also%20family%20support%20which%20affects%20the%20quality%20of%20speech%20and%20educational%20rehabilitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Bhatia%20urges%20parents%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CDo%20not%20ignore%20any%20warning%20signs%20or%20doubts.%20Just%20go%20and%20consult%20a%20doctor.%20Cochlear%20implants%20are%20nothing%20to%20be%20wary%20of%20%E2%80%93%20they%20are%20a%20well%20established%20technology%20and%20can%20change%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20life%20for%20the%20better%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20pictures%20courtesy%20The%20Hans%20Foundation)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708836709000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D343108%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22By%20spotting%20hearing%20loss%20in%20children%20early%20on%20and%20offering%20life-changing%20surgery%2C%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20(THF)%20has%20helped%20over%20900%20children%20with%20its%20Cochlear%20Implant%20Programme.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343108%2Fthe-hans-foundation-cochlear-implant-program-for-children-with-hearing-los