rocess%20hassle-free.%20Because%20of%20the%20polymer%2C%20farmers%20only%20have%20to%20irrigate%20the%20land%20once%20in%2025%20days%20in%20contrast%20to%20once%20in%2015%20days.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Akshay%20claims%20that%20over%2035%2C000%20farmers%20have%20benefitted%20from%20the%20product.%20As%20more%20and%20more%20farmers%20are%20adopting%20this%20new%20piece%20of%20wonder%2C%20Akshay%20says%20he%20feels%20it%20is%20a%20personal%20win.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20grown%20up%20watching%20what%20farmers%20have%20to%20endure%20because%20of%20products%20that%20do%20not%20perform%20well.%20I%E2%80%99m%20happy%20that%20I%20can%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708610946000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-1708603905.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D342901%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Akshay%20Shrivastav%2C%20a%20chemical%20engineer%2C%20launched%20'Navyakosh'%2C%20a%20unique%20fertiliser%20rich%20in%20microbes%20that%20can%20help%20farmers%20increase%20their%20productivity.%20He%20started%20his%20company%2C%20LCB%20Fertilizers%2C%20in%20his%20backyard%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic-induced%20lockdown.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342901%2Ffarmer-income-success-lcb-fertilizers-biofertiliser-navyakosh-akshay-shrivastav-iit-kanpur-labs%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98My%20Dad%E2%80%99s%20a%20Farmer%20%26amp%3B%20This%20Was%20a%20Dream%E2%80%99%3A%20Engineer%20Grows%20Rare%20%E2%80%98Yellow%20Dates%E2%80%99%2C%20Reaps%20Big%20Profits%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20of%20the%20youth%20in%20the%20country%20are%20heading%20towards%20corporate%20jobs%2C%20only%20a%20few%20turn%20towards%20farming.%20Affected%20by%20various%20factors%2C%20especially%20high%20risk%20and%20low%20profitability%2C%20no%20farmer%20would%20want%20his%20son%20to%20become%20a%20farmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20know%20that%20there%20is%20a%20certain%20perspective%20towards%20taking%20up%20farming.%20But%20I%20was%20very%20sure%20from%20the%20beginning%20of%20my%20career%20that%20I%20would%20end%20up%20in%20the%20agriculture%20industry%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342247%2Fmangaluru-man-quits-corporate-career-for-farming-exotic-fruits-vegetables-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20engineer-turned-agriprenuer%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Nagendra%20Naidu%20Dharmavarapu%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Farmties%20India%20Private%20Limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Nagendra%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20find%20one%E2%80%99s%20niche%20in%20farming%20to%20earn%20profits.%20He%20found%20his%20niche%20in%20Yellow%20Dates%2C%20a%20super%20food%2C%20which%20is%20earning%20him%20Rs%203.5%20lakhs%20per%20acre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntrigued%20by%20the%20product%20and%20how%20he%20found%20his%20market%2C%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20had%20a%20conversation%20with%20Nagendra%20where%20he%20recalls%20his%20initial%20days%20of%20brainstorming%20to%20make%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBack%20to%20his%20roots%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20into%20a%20family%20of%20farmers%2C%20Nagendra%20grew%20up%20in%20close%20proximity%20to%20the%20issues%20farmers%20faced%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20intimately%20familiar%20with%20these%20challenges%20and%20had%20grown%20up%20pondering%20potential%20solutions.%20In%20my%20mind%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20an%20agripreneur%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20while%20Nagendra%20was%20in%20an%20engineering%2