la-anganwadis-helps-bring-girls-to-school%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erenovating%20the%20school.%20%3C%2Fa%3ETowards%20this%2C%20he%20spent%20Rs%203%20lakh%20from%20his%20own%20pocket%2C%20using%20which%20he%20revamped%20the%20walls%20and%20washrooms%2C%20planted%20a%20garden%2C%20brought%20water%20to%20the%20school%2C%20and%20set%20up%20a%20library.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETransforming%20a%20neglected%20school%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Gopal%20was%20assigned%20to%20the%20middle%20school%2C%20what%20greeted%20him%20were%20a%20handful%20of%20students%20and%20four%20poorly%20lit%20classrooms%20masquerading%20as%20a%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20school%20was%20in%20a%20deplorable%20state%2C%20to%20put%20it%20mildly.%20The%20walls%20lacked%20paint%2C%20and%20there%20was%20a%20noticeable%20lack%20of%20enthusiasm%20in%20the%20students%E2%80%99%20eyes%2C%20which%20troubled%20me%20the%20most.%20However%2C%20I%20could%20empathise%20because%20even%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20study%20in%20such%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reflects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGopal%20explains%20that%20most%20of%20the%20students%20and%20residents%20hailed%20from%20villages%20near%20the%20Mohanpura%20Dam.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20construction%20of%20the%20dam%20forced%20these%20people%20to%20relocate.%20The%20Government%20built%20a%20few%20houses%20and%20roads%2C%20and%20labelled%20it%20Mohanpura%20Colony.%20However%20they%20did%20not%20create%20any%20employment%20for%20the%20people%20displaced%20who%20had%20lost%20their%20lands%20and%20had%20no%20avenue%20of%20income.%20So%20most%20of%20the%20people%20were%20worried%20about%20bringing%20food%20to%20the%20table%20at%20the%20time%2C%20and%20educational%20concerns%20were%20far%20from%20being%20in%20their%20mind%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src