20of%20District%20Collector%20Avi%20Prasad%2C%20who%20launched%20a%20unique%20initiative%20to%20fight%20against%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F163173%2Fposhan-abhiyaan-malnutrition-solution-india-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eissue%20of%20malnutrition%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20In%20a%20remarkable%20effort%2C%20he%20roped%20in%20the%20community%20members%20and%20encouraged%20them%20to%20adopt%20malnourished%20children%20to%20improve%20their%20nutritional%20status.%20Interestingly%2C%20this%20approach%20has%20helped%20the%20district%20reduce%20malnutrition%20by%20nearly%2030%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20conversation%20with%20us%2C%20the%20District%20Magistrate%20sheds%20light%20on%20how%20he%20aims%20at%20eradicating%20malnutrition%20in%20his%20district%20with%20this%20unique%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20every%20second%20child%20was%20malnourished%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20one%20of%20his%20visits%20to%20an%20%3Cem%3Eanganwadi%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecentre%20when%20IAS%20Avi%20Prasad%20saw%20a%20year-old%20Sakshi%20lying%20in%20her%20mother%E2%80%99s%20arms.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20looked%20very%20weak.%20After%20inquiring%2C%20I%20came%20to%20know%20that%20her%20father%20was%20unemployed%20and%20they%20could%20not%20afford%20to%20look%20after%20her%20nutritional%20requirements.%20She%20also%20developed%20a%20heart%20disease%20because%20of%20a%20lack%20of%20a%20proper%20diet%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20sought%20help%20from%20the%20community%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20industrialists%20wished%20to%20adopt%20that%20child.%20With%20his%20support%2C%20Sakshi%20underwent%20a%20hernia%20operation%20and%20was%20also%20provided%20with%20additional%20nutrition%20via%20a%20special%20nutrition%20kit.%20Because%20of%20the%20timely%20intervent